CensoArboreoController.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using CsvHelper;
using CsvHelper.Configuration;
using Ionic.Zip;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Http;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc;
using Microsoft.Extensions.Options;
using NetTopologySuite.Features;
using NetTopologySuite.Geometries;
using NetTopologySuite.IO.Esri;
using Newtonsoft.Json;
using SocialMedia.Api.Responses;
using SocialMedia.Api.Utils;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Dtos;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using SocialMedia.Infrastructure.Options;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Globalization;
using System.IO;
using System.IO.Compression;
using System.Linq;
using System.Text;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Api.Controllers
{
    [Authorize]
    [Produces("application/json")]
    [Route("api/[Controller]")]
    [ApiController]
    public class CensoArboreoController : ControllerBase
    {
        private readonly ICensoArboreoService _censoArboreoService;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;
        private readonly IOptions<ShapefileSettings> _shapefileSettings;

        public CensoArboreoController(ICensoArboreoService censoArboreoService, IMapper mapper, IOptions<ShapefileSettings> shapefileSettings)
        {
            this._censoArboreoService = censoArboreoService;
            this._mapper = mapper;
            _shapefileSettings = shapefileSettings;
        }

        [HttpGet(Name = nameof(GetCensoArboreos))]
        public IActionResult GetCensoArboreos([FromQuery] CensoArboreoQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var censos = _censoArboreoService.GetCensoArboreos(filters);
            var censoDtos = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<CensoArboreoDto>>(censos);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<CensoArboreoDto>>(censoDtos);
            var metaData = new Metadata
            {
                TotalCount = censos.TotalCount,
                PageSize = censos.PageSize,
                CurrentPage = censos.CurrentPage,
                TotalPages = censos.TotalPages,
                HasNextPage = censos.HasNextPage,
                HasPreviousPage = censos.HasPreviousPage,
            };

            response.Meta = metaData;
            Response.Headers.Add("X-Pagination", JsonConvert.SerializeObject(metaData));
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Get(Guid id)
        {
            var censo = await _censoArboreoService.GetCensoArboreo(id);
            var censoDto = _mapper.Map<CensoArboreoDto>(censo);
            var response = new ApiResponse<CensoArboreoDto>(censoDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPost]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Post(CensoArboreoDto censoArboreoDto)
        {
            var censo = _mapper.Map<CensoArboreo>(censoArboreoDto);
            await _censoArboreoService.InsertCensoArboreo(censo);
            censoArboreoDto = _mapper.Map<CensoArboreoDto>(censo);
            var response = new ApiResponse<CensoArboreoDto>(censoArboreoDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPut("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Put(Guid id, CensoArboreoDto censoArboreoDto)
        {
            var censo = _mapper.Map<CensoArboreo>(censoArboreoDto);
            censo.Id = id;
            await _censoArboreoService.UpdateCensoArboreo(censo);
            return Ok();
        }

        [HttpDelete("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Delete(Guid id)
        {
            try
            {
                await _censoArboreoService.DeleteCensoArboreo(id);
                return Ok();
            }
            catch (Exception ex)
            {
                Console.WriteLine(ex.ToString());
                return BadRequest();
            }
        }

        [HttpPost("LoadCensoWithImages")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> LoadCensoWithImages(
            List<IFormFile> files,
            [FromForm] string fullobject,
            [FromForm] string infofotos
        )
        {
            var mensaje = "files";

            var censoObj = JsonConvert.DeserializeObject<CensoArboreoDto>(fullobject);
            var rotationObj = JsonConvert.DeserializeObject<InfoFotosDto>(infofotos);
            // Crea una lista para almacenar los registros procesados

            censoObj.Fotos = new List<RegistroFotograficoCensoDto>();
            // Lee el archivo
            var i = 0;
            foreach (var file in files)
            {
                var foto = await HelperFiles.SaveFileAsync(file, rotationObj.Rotation[i]);
                censoObj.Fotos.Add(foto);
                i++;
            }

            try
            {
                var censo = _mapper.Map<CensoArboreo>(censoObj);
                await _censoArboreoService.InsertCensoArboreo(censo);
                censoObj = _mapper.Map<CensoArboreoDto>(censo);
                var response = new ApiResponse<CensoArboreoDto>(censoObj);
                return Ok(response);
            }
            catch (Exception ex)
            {
                return BadRequest();
            }
        }


        [HttpPut("UpdateLoadCensoWithImages/{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> UpdateLoadCensoWithImages(
            Guid id,
            List<IFormFile> files,
            [FromForm] string fullobject,
            [FromForm] string infofotos
        )
        {
            var mensaje = "files";

            var censoObj = JsonConvert.DeserializeObject<CensoArboreoDto>(fullobject);
            var rotationObj = JsonConvert.DeserializeObject<InfoFotosDto>(infofotos);
            // Crea una lista para almacenar los registros procesados
            var processedData = new List<(string CodigoAfiliado, int ValorLectura)>();
            //censoObj.Fotos = new List<RegistroFotograficoCensoArboreoDto>();
            // Lee el archivo
            var i = 0;
            foreach (var file in files)
            {
                var foto = await HelperFiles.SaveFileAsync(file, rotationObj.Rotation[i]);
                censoObj.Fotos.Add(foto);
                i++;
            }

            try
            {
                var censo = _mapper.Map<CensoArboreo>(censoObj);
                censo.Id = id;
                await _censoArboreoService.UpdateCensoArboreo(censo);
            }
            catch (Exception ex)
            {
                Console.WriteLine(ex.ToString());
                return BadRequest();
            }

            return Ok();
        }

        [HttpGet("export")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> ExportCensoArboreoCsv()
        {
            // Suponiendo que tienes un método para obtener tus datos del censo.
            var censusData = await this._censoArboreoService.ExportCensoArboreoData();

            // Configurar el MemoryStream para escribir el contenido CSV.
            var memoryStream = new MemoryStream();
            using (var streamWriter = new StreamWriter(memoryStream, new UTF8Encoding(encoderShouldEmitUTF8Identifier: true), leaveOpen: true)) // Usar UTF-8 con BOM
            using (var csvWriter = new CsvWriter(streamWriter, new CsvConfiguration(CultureInfo.InvariantCulture)
            {
                Delimiter = "|", // Establecer el delimitador como punto y coma
                Encoding = new UTF8Encoding(encoderShouldEmitUTF8Identifier: true) // Asegurarse de que CsvWriter también use UTF-8
            }))
            {
                // Escribir los registros en el CSV.
                csvWriter.WriteRecords(censusData);

                // Vaciar el escritor para asegurarse de que todos los datos se escriban en MemoryStream.
                await streamWriter.FlushAsync();

                // Restablecer la posición del MemoryStream a 0 para comenzar a leer desde el principio.
                memoryStream.Position = 0;
            }

            // Crear un FileStreamResult que es un ActionResult.
            // Está leyendo el MemoryStream y devuelve un archivo con el tipo de contenido especificado.
            // FileStreamResult se encargará de desechar el stream.
            var result = new FileStreamResult(memoryStream, "text/csv")
            {
                FileDownloadName = "census_data.csv"
            };

            return result;
        }


        [HttpGet("exportShape")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> ExportCensoArboreoShape()
        {
            // Asumiendo que tienes un método para obtener tus datos del censo.
            var censusData = await this._censoArboreoService.ExportCensoArboreoData();

            // Asegúrate de que los shapefiles han sido creados en filesDirectory antes de llamar a este método
            await this.ExportCensoArboreoDataToShapefile(censusData.ToList());

            // Define la ruta del directorio que quieres comprimir.
            var filesDirectory = _shapefileSettings.Value.OutputDirectory;

            // Define la ruta del archivo ZIP que se creará.
            var zipPath = Path.Combine(_shapefileSettings.Value.ZipOutputDirectory, _shapefileSettings.Value.ZipFileName);

            // Usar MemoryStream para almacenar el ZIP temporalmente.
            var zipStream = new MemoryStream();

            try
            {
                // Crear un nuevo archivo ZIP.
                using (Ionic.Zip.ZipFile zip = new Ionic.Zip.ZipFile())
                {
                    // Añadir el directorio al archivo ZIP.
                    zip.AddDirectory(filesDirectory);
                    // Guardar el archivo ZIP en el MemoryStream.
                    zip.Save(zipStream);
                }

                // Establecer la posición del stream a 0 para leer desde el principio.
                zipStream.Position = 0;

                // Devolver el stream como un archivo para descargar.
                return File(zipStream, "application/zip", _shapefileSettings.Value.ZipFileName);
            }
            catch
            {
                zipStream.Dispose(); // Asegúrate de liberar los recursos en caso de una excepción.
                throw;
            }
        }
        private async Task<bool> ExportCensoArboreoDataToShapefile(List<CensoArboreoCSV> censoArboreoData)
        {
            // Preparar la colección de features
            var features = new FeatureCollection();

            // Definir la fábrica de geometría
            var geometryFactory = new GeometryFactory(new PrecisionModel(), 4326); // SRID 4326 es para WGS84

            foreach (var item in censoArboreoData)
            {
                try
                {
                    // Crear punto geográfico para la feature basado en Latitud y Longitud
                    var longitud = Convert.ToDouble(item.Longitud);
                    var latitud = Convert.ToDouble(item.Latitud);

                    var point = geometryFactory.CreatePoint(new Coordinate(longitud, latitud));

                    var attributesTable = new AttributesTable();

                    // Añadir todas las propiedades a attributesTable
                    attributesTable.Add("ALTITUD", item.Altitud);
                    attributesTable.Add("LAT", item.Latitud);
                    attributesTable.Add("LONG", item.Longitud);
                    attributesTable.Add("ESTE", item.Este);
                    attributesTable.Add("NORTE", item.Norte);
                    attributesTable.Add("CIUDAD", item.Ciudad);
                    attributesTable.Add("COMUNA", item.Comuna);
                    attributesTable.Add("BARRIO", item.Barrio);
                    attributesTable.Add("APEN_CITES", item.ApendiceCites);
                    attributesTable.Add("CAT_M_R192", item.CategoriaMinisterioResolucion01922014);
                    attributesTable.Add("CAT_UICN", item.CategoriaUicn);
                    attributesTable.Add("ESP_END", item.EspecieEndemica);
                    attributesTable.Add("ALT_TOTA", item.AlturaTotal.ToString());
                    attributesTable.Add("ALTITU", item.AltitudASNM.ToString());
                    attributesTable.Add("ALT_COM", item.AlturaComercial.ToString());
                    attributesTable.Add("ALT_COPA", item.AlturaCopa.ToString());
                    attributesTable.Add("CUADRILLA", item.Cuadrilla);
                    attributesTable.Add("DAP_1", item.DAP.ToString());
                    attributesTable.Add("DAP_2", item.DAP2.ToString());
                    attributesTable.Add("DAP_3", item.DAP3.ToString());
                    attributesTable.Add("DAP_4", item.DAP4.ToString());
                    attributesTable.Add("DAP_TOTAL", item.DAPTOTAL.ToString());
                    attributesTable.Add("NDAP_TOTA", item.NDAPTOTAL.ToString());
                    attributesTable.Add("DPTO", item.Departamento);
                    attributesTable.Add("D_COPA_EC", item.DiametroCopa.ToString());
                    attributesTable.Add("ESPECIE", item.Especie);
                    attributesTable.Add("EST_SANI", item.EstadoFitosanitario);
                    attributesTable.Add("EST_MADU", item.EstadoMadurez);
                    attributesTable.Add("Familia", item.Familia);
                    attributesTable.Add("Fecha", item.Fecha.ToString());
                    attributesTable.Add("FORM_COPA", item.FormaCopa);
                    attributesTable.Add("GENERO", item.Genero);
                    attributesTable.Add("INF_AFEC", item.InfraestructuraAfectada);
                    attributesTable.Add("NOM_CIENT", item.NombreCientifico);
                    attributesTable.Add("NOM_COMUN", item.NombreComun);
                    attributesTable.Add("NROFUSTE", item.NumeroFustes.ToString());
                    attributesTable.Add("N_ARBOL", item.NumeroIndividuoId);
                    attributesTable.Add("OBS", item.Observacion);
                    attributesTable.Add("OFORM_COP", item.ObservacionCopa);
                    attributesTable.Add("O_INF_AFE", item.ObservacionInfraestructuraAfectada);
                    attributesTable.Add("OTIPOEMPL", item.ObservacionTipoEmplazamiento);
                    attributesTable.Add("ORDEN", item.Orden);
                    attributesTable.Add("ORIGEN", item.Origen);
                    attributesTable.Add("RMANSILV", item.RecomendacionesParaManejoSilvicultural);
                    attributesTable.Add("TIPOAGLO", item.TipoAglomeracion);
                    attributesTable.Add("TIPO_EMPL", item.TipoEmplazamiento);
                    attributesTable.Add("TIP_INDI", item.TipoIndividuoForestal);
                    // ... (Incluye todas las otras propiedades relevantes)

                    var feature = new Feature(point, attributesTable);
                    features.Add(feature);
                }
                catch (Exception e)
                {
                    throw;
                }

            }

            Shapefile.WriteAllFeatures(features, $"{_shapefileSettings.Value.OutputDirectory}\\{_shapefileSettings.Value.ZipFileName}");

            return true;
        }


        [HttpGet("GetUbicacionArboles")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> GetUbicacionArboles()
        {
            var censusData = await this._censoArboreoService.GetAllCoordenadas();
            var barriosDto = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<CoordenadaDto>>(censusData);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<CoordenadaDto>>(barriosDto);

            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet("GetUbicacionArbolesCercanos")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> GetUbicacionArbolesCercanos(int lat = 0, int lon = 0, int dist = 0)
        {
            var censusData = await this._censoArboreoService.GetCoordenadasCercanas(lat, lon, dist);
            var barriosDto = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<CoordenadaDto>>(censusData);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<CoordenadaDto>>(barriosDto);

            return Ok(response);
        }


        [HttpPost]
        [Route("cargarArchivo")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> CargarArchivo(IFormFile file, [FromForm] int PeriodoId)
        {
            if (file == null || file.Length == 0)
            {
                throw new BusinessException("No se proporcionó ningún archivo para cargar.");
            }
            var processedData = new List<CensoArboreoCSV>();

            using (var reader = new StreamReader(file.OpenReadStream(), Encoding.UTF8)) // Asegúrese de usar el encoding correcto para caracteres especiales como 'ñ'.
            {
                // Omita la cabecera si existe, suponiendo que la primera línea es la cabecera
                // Si no hay cabecera, comente la siguiente línea.
                await reader.ReadLineAsync();

                string line;
                while ((line = await reader.ReadLineAsync()) != null)
                {
                    var parts = line.Split('|');
                    if (parts.Length != 48) // Asegúrese de que el número de partes sea igual al número de propiedades en CensoArboreoCSV
                    {
                        // Omitir líneas inválidas
                        continue;
                    }

                    var record = new CensoArboreoCSV
                    {
                        NumeroIndividuoId = parts[0],
                        AlturaTotal = decimal.Parse(parts[1]),
                        AlturaComercial = decimal.Parse(parts[2]),
                        Cuadrilla = parts[3],
                        FormaCopa = parts[4],
                        DiametroCopa = decimal.Parse(parts[5]),
                        AlturaCopa = decimal.Parse(parts[6]),
                        ObservacionCopa = parts[7],
                        DAP = decimal.Parse(parts[8]),
                        DAP2 = decimal.Parse(parts[9]),
                        DAP3 = decimal.Parse(parts[10]),
                        DAP4 = decimal.Parse(parts[11]),
                        NDAPTOTAL = decimal.Parse(parts[12]),
                        DAPTOTAL = decimal.Parse(parts[13]),
                        NumeroFustes = decimal.Parse(parts[14]),
                        NombreComun = parts[15],
                        NombreCientifico = parts[16],
                        Orden = parts[17],
                        Familia = parts[18],
                        Genero = parts[19],
                        Especie = parts[20],
                        AltitudASNM = decimal.Parse(parts[21]),
                        EstadoFitosanitario = parts[22],
                        EstadoMadurez = parts[23],
                        TipoIndividuoForestal = parts[24],
                        Departamento = parts[25],
                        Ciudad = parts[26],
                        TipoAglomeracion = parts[27],
                        Barrio = parts[28],
                        Comuna = parts[29],
                        TipoEmplazamiento = parts[30],
                        ObservacionTipoEmplazamiento = parts[31],
                        InfraestructuraAfectada = parts[32],
                        ObservacionInfraestructuraAfectada = parts[33],
                        ApendiceCites = parts[34],
                        CategoriaUicn = parts[35],
                        CategoriaMinisterioResolucion01922014 = parts[36],
                        EspecieEndemica = parts[37],
                        Origen = parts[38],
                        Observacion = parts[39],
                        Fecha = DateTime.Parse(parts[40]), // Asegúrese de que el formato de fecha coincide con el del archivo CSV
                                                           // Las siguientes propiedades parecen estar faltando en el orden inicial dado.
                                                           // Asegúrate de agregarlos en el orden correcto según tu CSV
                        RecomendacionesParaManejoSilvicultural = parts[41],
                        Latitud = parts[42],
                        Longitud = parts[43],
                        Altitud = parts[44],
                        Norte = parts[45],
                        Este = parts[46],
                        IsGuadua = parts[47],

                    };

                    processedData.Add(record);
                }
            }

            await this._censoArboreoService.CargarArchivo(processedData);

            return Ok();
        }

    }
}

---------------------------------------
ClasificacionController.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Cors;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc;
using Newtonsoft.Json;
using SocialMedia.Api.Responses;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Dtos;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using SocialMedia.Core.Services;
using SocialMedia.Infrastructure.Interfaces;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Net;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Api.Controllers
{
    [ApiController]
    [Route("api/[controller]")]
    [EnableCors("AllowAllOrigins")]
    public class ClasificacionController : ControllerBase
    {
        private readonly IClasificacionService _ClasificacionService;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;
        private readonly IUriService _uriService;

        public ClasificacionController(IClasificacionService ClasificacionService, IMapper mapper, IUriService uriService)
        {
            _ClasificacionService = ClasificacionService;
            _mapper = mapper;
            _uriService = uriService;
        }

        [HttpGet]
        [Route("getAll")]
        public IActionResult getAll()
        {
            var barriosList = _ClasificacionService.GetAll();
            var barriosDto = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<ClasificacionDto>>(barriosList);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<ClasificacionDto>>(barriosDto);

            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet(Name = nameof(GetClasificacions))]
        [ProducesResponseType((int)HttpStatusCode.OK, Type = typeof(ApiResponse<IEnumerable<ClasificacionDto>>))]
        [ProducesResponseType((int)HttpStatusCode.BadRequest)]
        public IActionResult GetClasificacions([FromQuery] ClasificacionQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var Clasificacions = _ClasificacionService.Get(filters);
            var ClasificacionDto = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<ClasificacionDto>>(Clasificacions);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<ClasificacionDto>>(ClasificacionDto);

            var metaData = new Metadata
            {
                TotalCount = Clasificacions.TotalCount,
                PageSize = Clasificacions.PageSize,
                CurrentPage = Clasificacions.CurrentPage,
                TotalPages = Clasificacions.TotalPages,
                HasNextPage = Clasificacions.HasNextPage,
                HasPreviousPage = Clasificacions.HasPreviousPage,
            };

            response.Meta = metaData;
            Response.Headers.Add("X-Pagination", JsonConvert.SerializeObject(metaData));

            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Get(Guid id)
        {
            var Clasificacion = await _ClasificacionService.Get(id);
            var ClasificacionDto = _mapper.Map<ClasificacionDto>(Clasificacion);
            var response = new ApiResponse<ClasificacionDto>(ClasificacionDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPost]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Post(ClasificacionDto ClasificacionDto)
        {
            var Clasificacion = _mapper.Map<Clasificacion>(ClasificacionDto);

            await _ClasificacionService.Insert(Clasificacion);

            ClasificacionDto = _mapper.Map<ClasificacionDto>(Clasificacion);

            var response = new ApiResponse<ClasificacionDto>(ClasificacionDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPut("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Put(Guid id, ClasificacionDto ClasificacionDto)
        {
            var Clasificacion = _mapper.Map<Clasificacion>(ClasificacionDto);
            Clasificacion.Id = id;

            await _ClasificacionService.Update(Clasificacion);

            return Ok();
        }

        [HttpDelete("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Delete(Guid id)
        {
            await _ClasificacionService.Delete(id);
            return Ok();
        }
    }
}

---------------------------------------
DetalleController.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc;
using SocialMedia.Api.Responses;
using SocialMedia.Core.Dtos;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Threading.Tasks;
using System;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using Newtonsoft.Json;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;

namespace SocialMedia.Api.Controllers
{

    [Authorize]
    [Produces("application/json")]
    [Route("api/[Controller]")]
    [ApiController]
    public class DetalleController : ControllerBase
    {
        private readonly IDetalleService _detalleService;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;

        public DetalleController(IDetalleService detalleService, IMapper mapper)
        {
            this._detalleService = detalleService;
            this._mapper = mapper;
        }

        [HttpGet(Name = nameof(GetDetalles))]
        public IActionResult GetDetalles([FromQuery] DetalleQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var detalles = _detalleService.GetDetalles(filters);
            var detallesDtos = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<DetalleDto>>(detalles);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<DetalleDto>>(detallesDtos);
            // Lógica para agregar metadatos y cabeceras de paginación.

            var metaData = new Metadata
            {
                TotalCount = detalles.TotalCount,
                PageSize = detalles.PageSize,
                CurrentPage = detalles.CurrentPage,
                TotalPages = detalles.TotalPages,
                HasNextPage = detalles.HasNextPage,
                HasPreviousPage = detalles.HasPreviousPage,
            };

            response.Meta = metaData;
            Response.Headers.Add("X-Pagination", JsonConvert.SerializeObject(metaData));

            return Ok(response);
            
        }

        [HttpGet("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Get(Guid id)
        {
            var censo = await _detalleService.GetDetalle(id);
            var censoDto = _mapper.Map<DetalleDto>(censo);
            var response = new ApiResponse<DetalleDto>(censoDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet("GetByMaestra/{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> GetByMaestra(Guid id)
        {
            var censo = await _detalleService.GetDetallesByMaestra(id);
            var censoDto = _mapper.Map<List<DetalleDto>>(censo);
            var response = new ApiResponse<List<DetalleDto>>(censoDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPost]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Post(DetalleDto detalleDto)
        {
            var censo = _mapper.Map<Detalle>(detalleDto);
            await _detalleService.InsertDetalle(censo);
            detalleDto = _mapper.Map<DetalleDto>(censo);
            var response = new ApiResponse<DetalleDto>(detalleDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPut("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Put(Guid id, DetalleDto detalleDto)
        {
            var censo = _mapper.Map<Detalle>(detalleDto);
            censo.Id = id;
            await _detalleService.UpdateDetalle(censo);
            return Ok();
        }

        [HttpDelete("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Delete(Guid id)
        {
            await _detalleService.DeleteDetalle(id);
            return Ok();
        }
    }
}

---------------------------------------
EspaciosPotencialesController.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc;
using SocialMedia.Api.Responses;
using SocialMedia.Core.Dtos;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Threading.Tasks;
using System;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using Newtonsoft.Json;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Http;
using System.IO;
using SocialMedia.Api.Utils;
using CsvHelper.Configuration;
using CsvHelper;
using System.Globalization;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;

namespace SocialMedia.Api.Controllers
{
    [Authorize]
    [Produces("application/json")]
    [Route("api/[Controller]")]
    [ApiController]
    public class EspaciosPotencialesController : ControllerBase
    {
        private readonly IEspaciosPotencialesService _espaciosPotencialesService;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;

        public EspaciosPotencialesController(
            IEspaciosPotencialesService espaciosPotencialesService,
            IMapper mapper
        )
        {
            this._espaciosPotencialesService = espaciosPotencialesService;
            this._mapper = mapper;
        }

        [HttpPost]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Post(EspaciosPotencialesDto espaciosPotencialesDto)
        {
            var espacios = _mapper.Map<EspaciosPotenciales>(espaciosPotencialesDto);
            await _espaciosPotencialesService.InsertEspaciosPotenciales(espacios);
            espaciosPotencialesDto = _mapper.Map<EspaciosPotencialesDto>(espacios);

            var response = new ApiResponse<EspaciosPotencialesDto>(espaciosPotencialesDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPut("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Put(Guid id, EspaciosPotencialesDto espaciosPotencialesDto)
        {
            var espacios = _mapper.Map<EspaciosPotenciales>(espaciosPotencialesDto);
            espacios.Id = id;
            await _espaciosPotencialesService.UpdateEspaciosPotenciales(espacios);
            return Ok();
        }

        [HttpGet("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Get(Guid id)
        {
            var espacios = await _espaciosPotencialesService.GetEspaciosPotenciales(id);
            var espaciosDto = _mapper.Map<EspaciosPotencialesDto>(espacios);
            var response = new ApiResponse<EspaciosPotencialesDto>(espaciosDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet(Name = nameof(GetEspaciosPotenciales))]
        public IActionResult GetEspaciosPotenciales(
            [FromQuery] EspaciosPotencialesQueryFilter filters
        )
        {
            var espacios = _espaciosPotencialesService.GetEspaciosPotenciales(filters);
            var espaciosDto = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<EspaciosPotencialesDto>>(espacios);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<EspaciosPotencialesDto>>(espaciosDto);

            var metaData = new Metadata
            {
                TotalCount = espacios.TotalCount,
                PageSize = espacios.PageSize,
                CurrentPage = espacios.CurrentPage,
                TotalPages = espacios.TotalPages,
                HasNextPage = espacios.HasNextPage,
                HasPreviousPage = espacios.HasPreviousPage,
            };

            response.Meta = metaData;
            Response.Headers.Add("X-Pagination", JsonConvert.SerializeObject(metaData));

            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpDelete("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Delete(Guid id)
        {
            await _espaciosPotencialesService.DeleteEspaciosPotenciales(id);
            return Ok();
        }

        [HttpPost("LoadEspacioWithImages")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> LoadEspaciosWithImages(
            List<IFormFile> files,
            [FromForm] string fullobject,
            [FromForm] string infofotos
        )
        {
            var mensaje = "files";

            var espaciosObj = JsonConvert.DeserializeObject<EspaciosPotencialesDto>(fullobject);
            var rotationObj = JsonConvert.DeserializeObject<InfoFotosDto>(infofotos);

            espaciosObj.Fotos = new List<RegistroFotograficoEspacioDto>();

            var i = 0;
            foreach (var file in files)
            {
                var fotoCenso = await HelperFiles.SaveFileAsync(file, rotationObj.Rotation[i]);
                var foroEspacio = new RegistroFotograficoEspacioDto()
                {
                    Nombre = fotoCenso.Nombre,
                    Url = fotoCenso.Url
                };
                espaciosObj.Fotos.Add(foroEspacio);
                i++;
               
            }
            try
            {
                var espacios = _mapper.Map<EspaciosPotenciales>(espaciosObj);
                await _espaciosPotencialesService.InsertEspaciosPotenciales(espacios);
                espaciosObj = _mapper.Map<EspaciosPotencialesDto>(espacios);
                var response = new ApiResponse<EspaciosPotencialesDto>(espaciosObj);
                return Ok(response);
            }
            catch (Exception ex)
            {
                return BadRequest();
            }
        }

        [HttpPut("UpdateLoadEspacioWithImages/{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> UpdateLoadEspacioWithImages(
            Guid id,
            List<IFormFile> files,
            [FromForm] string fullobject,
            [FromForm] string infofotos
        )
        {
            var espaciosObj = JsonConvert.DeserializeObject<EspaciosPotencialesDto>(fullobject);
            var rotationObj = JsonConvert.DeserializeObject<InfoFotosDto>(infofotos);

            var processedData = new List<(string CodigoAfiliado, int ValorLectura)>();
            var i = 0;
            foreach (var file in files)
            {


                var fotoCenso = await HelperFiles.SaveFileAsync(file, rotationObj.Rotation[i]);
                var foroEspacio = new RegistroFotograficoEspacioDto()
                {
                    Nombre = fotoCenso.Nombre,
                    Url = fotoCenso.Url
                };
                espaciosObj.Fotos.Add(foroEspacio);
                i++;
            }

            try
            {
                var espacios = _mapper.Map<EspaciosPotenciales>(espaciosObj);
                espacios.Id = id;
                await _espaciosPotencialesService.UpdateEspaciosPotenciales(espacios);
            }
            catch (Exception ex)
            {
                Console.WriteLine(ex.ToString());
                return BadRequest();
            }

            return Ok();
        }

        [HttpGet("export")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> ExportEspacioPotencialCsv()
        {
            // Assuming you have a method to get your census data.
            var censusData = await this._espaciosPotencialesService.ExportEspaciosPotencialesData();

            // Set up the memory stream to write the CSV content into.
            var memoryStream = new MemoryStream();
            using (var streamWriter = new StreamWriter(memoryStream, leaveOpen: true)) // Keep the stream open
            using (var csvWriter = new CsvWriter(streamWriter, new CsvConfiguration(CultureInfo.InvariantCulture)
            {
                Delimiter = "|" // Set the delimiter to semicolon
            }
              ))
            {
                // Write the records to the CSV.
                csvWriter.WriteRecords(censusData);

                // Flush the writer to make sure all data is written to the MemoryStream.
                await streamWriter.FlushAsync();

                // Reset the memory stream position to 0 to start reading from the beginning.
                memoryStream.Position = 0;
            }

            // Create a FileStreamResult which is an ActionResult.
            // It's reading the MemoryStream and returns a file with the specified content type.
            // The FileStreamResult will take care of disposing the stream.
            var result = new FileStreamResult(memoryStream, "text/csv")
            {
                FileDownloadName = "espacios_data.csv"
            };

            return result;
        }

       
    }
}

ImagesController.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc;
using SocialMedia.Api.Responses;
using SocialMedia.Core.Dtos;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Threading.Tasks;
using System;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using Newtonsoft.Json;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using System.IO;
using SocialMedia.Api.Utils;

namespace SocialMedia.Api.Controllers
{

    [Authorize]
    [Produces("application/json")]
    [Route("api/[Controller]")]
    [ApiController]
    public class ImagesController : ControllerBase
    {
        private readonly IDetalleService _detalleService;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;

        public ImagesController(IDetalleService detalleService, IMapper mapper)
        {
            this._detalleService = detalleService;
            this._mapper = mapper;
        }

        [HttpGet("{imageName}")]
        public IActionResult GetImage(string imageName)
        {
            // Lógica para buscar y servir la imagen con el nombre proporcionado
            var bytes = HelperFiles.LoadImage(imageName);
            if (bytes != null)
                return File(bytes, "image/jpeg");

            return NotFound(); // Devuelve NotFound si la imagen no se encuentra
        }
    }
}

MaestraController.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc;
using SocialMedia.Api.Responses;
using SocialMedia.Core.Dtos;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Threading.Tasks;
using System;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using Newtonsoft.Json;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using System.Net;

namespace SocialMedia.Api.Controllers
{

    [Authorize]
    [Produces("application/json")]
    [Route("api/[Controller]")]
    [ApiController]
    public class MaestraController : ControllerBase
    {
        private readonly IMaestraService _maestraService;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;

        public MaestraController(IMaestraService maestraService, IMapper mapper)
        {
            this._maestraService = maestraService;
            this._mapper = mapper;
        }

        [HttpGet(Name = nameof(GetMaestras))]
        [ProducesResponseType((int)HttpStatusCode.OK, Type = typeof(ApiResponse<IEnumerable<MaestraDto>>))]
        [ProducesResponseType((int)HttpStatusCode.BadRequest)]
        public IActionResult GetMaestras([FromQuery] MaestraQueryFilter filters)
        {

            var maestras = _maestraService.GetMaestras(filters);
            var maestraDto = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<MaestraDto>>(maestras);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<MaestraDto>>(maestraDto);

            var metaData = new Metadata
            {
                TotalCount = maestras.TotalCount,
                PageSize = maestras.PageSize,
                CurrentPage = maestras.CurrentPage,
                TotalPages = maestras.TotalPages,
                HasNextPage = maestras.HasNextPage,
                HasPreviousPage = maestras.HasPreviousPage,
            };

            response.Meta = metaData;
            Response.Headers.Add("X-Pagination", JsonConvert.SerializeObject(metaData));

            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Get(Guid id)
        {
            var maestra = await _maestraService.GetMaestra(id);
            var maestraDto = _mapper.Map<MaestraDto>(maestra);
            var response = new ApiResponse<MaestraDto>(maestraDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }
        [HttpGet("GetAll")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> GetAll()
        {
            var maestra = await _maestraService.GetAll();
            var maestraDto = _mapper.Map<List<MaestraDto>>(maestra);
            var response = new ApiResponse<List<MaestraDto>>(maestraDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }
        [HttpPost]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Post(MaestraDto maestraDto)
        {
            var maestra = _mapper.Map<Maestra>(maestraDto);

            await _maestraService.InsertMaestra(maestra);

            maestraDto = _mapper.Map<MaestraDto>(maestra);

            var response = new ApiResponse<MaestraDto>(maestraDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPut("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Put(Guid id, MaestraDto maestraDto)
        {
            var maestra = _mapper.Map<Maestra>(maestraDto);
            maestra.Id = id;

            await _maestraService.UpdateMaestra(maestra);

            return Ok();
        }

        [HttpDelete("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Delete(Guid id)
        {
            await _maestraService.DeleteMaestra(id);
            return Ok();
        }
    }
}

ModulesController.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using Azure;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc;
using Newtonsoft.Json;
using SocialMedia.Api.Responses;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Dtos;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using SocialMedia.Infrastructure.Interfaces;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Net;
using System.Threading.Tasks;
using System;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Cors;
using SocialMedia.Core.Services;

namespace SocialMedia.Api.Controllers
{
    [ApiController]
    [Route("api/[controller]")]
    [EnableCors("AllowAllOrigins")]
    public class ModulesController : ControllerBase
    {
        private readonly IModuleService _moduleService;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;
        private readonly IUriService _uriService;

        public ModulesController(IModuleService moduleService, IMapper mapper, IUriService uriService)
        {
            _moduleService = moduleService;
            _mapper = mapper;
            _uriService = uriService;
        }

        [HttpGet]
        [Route("getAll")]
        public IActionResult getAll()
        {
            var barriosList = _moduleService.GetAll();
            var barriosDto = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<ModulesDto>>(barriosList);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<ModulesDto>>(barriosDto);

            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet(Name = nameof(GetModules))]
        [ProducesResponseType((int)HttpStatusCode.OK, Type = typeof(ApiResponse<IEnumerable<ModulesDto>>))]
        [ProducesResponseType((int)HttpStatusCode.BadRequest)]
        public IActionResult GetModules([FromQuery] ModulesQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var Modules = _moduleService.Get(filters);
            var ModulesDto = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<ModulesDto>>(Modules);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<ModulesDto>>(ModulesDto);

            var metaData = new Metadata
            {
                TotalCount = Modules.TotalCount,
                PageSize = Modules.PageSize,
                CurrentPage = Modules.CurrentPage,
                TotalPages = Modules.TotalPages,
                HasNextPage = Modules.HasNextPage,
                HasPreviousPage = Modules.HasPreviousPage,
            };

            response.Meta = metaData;
            Response.Headers.Add("X-Pagination", JsonConvert.SerializeObject(metaData));

            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Get(Guid id)
        {
            var Module = await _moduleService.Get(id);
            var ModuleDto = _mapper.Map<ModulesDto>(Module);
            var response = new ApiResponse<ModulesDto>(ModuleDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPost]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Post(ModulesDto ModulesDto)
        {
            var Module = _mapper.Map<Modules>(ModulesDto);

            await _moduleService.Insert(Module);

            ModulesDto = _mapper.Map<ModulesDto>(Module);

            var response = new ApiResponse<ModulesDto>(ModulesDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPut("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Put(Guid id, ModulesDto ModulesDto)
        {
            var Module = _mapper.Map<Modules>(ModulesDto);
            Module.Id = id;

            await _moduleService.Update(Module);

            return Ok();
        }

        [HttpDelete("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Delete(Guid id)
        {
            await _moduleService.Delete(id);
            return Ok();
        }
    }
}

---------------------------------------
PostController.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Cors;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc;
using Newtonsoft.Json;
using SocialMedia.Api.Responses;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Dtos;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using SocialMedia.Infrastructure.Interfaces;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Net;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Api.Controllers
{
    [Authorize]
    [Produces("application/json")]
    [Route("api/[Controller]")]
    [ApiController]
    [EnableCors("AllowAllOrigins")]
    public class PostController : ControllerBase
    {
        private readonly IPostService _postService;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;
        private readonly IUriService _uriService;

        public PostController(IPostService postService, IMapper mapper, IUriService uriService)
        {
            this._postService = postService;
            this._mapper = mapper;
            _uriService = uriService;
        }

        [HttpGet(Name = nameof(GetPosts))]
        [ProducesResponseType((int)HttpStatusCode.OK, Type = typeof(ApiResponse<IEnumerable<PostDto>>))]
        [ProducesResponseType((int)HttpStatusCode.BadRequest, Type = typeof(ApiResponse<IEnumerable<PostDto>>))]
        public IActionResult GetPosts([FromQuery] PostQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var posts = _postService.GetPosts(filters);
            var postDto = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<PostDto>>(posts);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<PostDto>>(postDto);

            var metaData = new Metadata
            {
                TotalCount = posts.TotalCount,
                PageSize = posts.PageSize,
                CurrentPage = posts.CurrentPage,
                TotalPages = posts.TotalPages,
                HasNextPage = posts.HasNextPage,
                HasPreviousPage = posts.HasPreviousPage,
            };

            response.Meta = metaData;
            Response.Headers.Add("X-Pagination", JsonConvert.SerializeObject(metaData));

            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Get(Guid id)
        {
            var post = await _postService.GetPost(id);
            var postDto = _mapper.Map<PostDto>(post);
            var response = new ApiResponse<PostDto>(postDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPost]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Post(PostDto postDto)
        {
            var post = _mapper.Map<Post>(postDto);

            await _postService.InsertPost(post);

            postDto = _mapper.Map<PostDto>(post);

            var response = new ApiResponse<PostDto>(postDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPut]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Put(Guid id, PostDto postDto)
        {
            var post = _mapper.Map<Post>(postDto);
            postDto.Id = id;

            await _postService.UpdatePost(post);

            return Ok();
        }

        [HttpDelete("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Detele(Guid id)
        {
            await _postService.DeletePost(id);

            return Ok();
        }
    }
}

---------------------------------------
RolesController.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using Azure;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc;
using Newtonsoft.Json;
using SocialMedia.Api.Responses;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Dtos;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using SocialMedia.Infrastructure.Interfaces;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Net;
using System.Threading.Tasks;
using System;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Cors;

namespace SocialMedia.Api.Controllers
{
    [ApiController]
    [Route("api/[controller]")]
    [EnableCors("AllowAllOrigins")]
    public class RolesController : ControllerBase
    {
        private readonly IRolesService _rolesService;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;
        private readonly IUriService _uriService;

        public RolesController(IRolesService rolesService, IMapper mapper, IUriService uriService)
        {
            _rolesService = rolesService;
            _mapper = mapper;
            _uriService = uriService;
        }

        [HttpGet]
        [Route("getAll")]
        public IActionResult getAll()
        {
            var barriosList = _rolesService.GetAll();
            var barriosDto = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<RolesDto>>(barriosList);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<RolesDto>>(barriosDto);

            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet(Name = nameof(GetRoles))]
        [ProducesResponseType((int)HttpStatusCode.OK, Type = typeof(ApiResponse<IEnumerable<RolesDto>>))]
        [ProducesResponseType((int)HttpStatusCode.BadRequest)]
        public IActionResult GetRoles([FromQuery] RolesQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var roles = _rolesService.Get(filters);
            var rolesDto = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<RolesDto>>(roles);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<RolesDto>>(rolesDto);

            var metaData = new Metadata
            {
                TotalCount = roles.TotalCount,
                PageSize = roles.PageSize,
                CurrentPage = roles.CurrentPage,
                TotalPages = roles.TotalPages,
                HasNextPage = roles.HasNextPage,
                HasPreviousPage = roles.HasPreviousPage,
            };

            response.Meta = metaData;
            Response.Headers.Add("X-Pagination", JsonConvert.SerializeObject(metaData));

            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Get(Guid id)
        {
            var role = await _rolesService.Get(id);
            var roleDto = _mapper.Map<RolesDto>(role);
            var response = new ApiResponse<RolesDto>(roleDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPost]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Post(RolesDto rolesDto)
        {
            var role = _mapper.Map<Roles>(rolesDto);

            await _rolesService.Insert(role);

            rolesDto = _mapper.Map<RolesDto>(role);

            var response = new ApiResponse<RolesDto>(rolesDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPut("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Put(Guid id, RolesDto rolesDto)
        {
            var role = _mapper.Map<Roles>(rolesDto);
            role.Id = id;

            await _rolesService.Update(role);

            return Ok();
        }

        [HttpDelete("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Delete(Guid id)
        {
            await _rolesService.Delete(id);
            return Ok();
        }
    }
}

            return Ok();

    }

SecurityController.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Cors;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc;
using SocialMedia.Api.Responses;
using SocialMedia.Core.DTOs;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Enumerations;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Infrastructure.Interfaces;
using System;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Api.Controllers
{
    [Authorize(Roles = nameof(RoleType.Administrator))]
    [Produces("application/json")]
    [Route("api/[controller]")]
    [ApiController]
    [EnableCors("AllowAllOrigins")]
    public class SecurityController : ControllerBase
    {
        private readonly ISecurityService _securityService;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;
        private readonly IPasswordService _passwordService;

        public SecurityController(ISecurityService securityService, IMapper mapper, IPasswordService passwordService)
        {
            _securityService = securityService;
            _mapper = mapper;
            _passwordService = passwordService;
        }

        /// <summary>
        /// Create User Login.
        /// </summary>
        /// <param name="securityDto"></param>
        /// <returns></returns>
        [HttpPost]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Post(SecurityDto securityDto)
        {
            var security = _mapper.Map<Security>(securityDto);

            security.Password = _passwordService.Hash(security.Password);
            await _securityService.RegisterUser(security);

            securityDto = _mapper.Map<SecurityDto>(security);
            var response = new ApiResponse<SecurityDto>(securityDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPut("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Put(Guid id, SecurityDto securityDto)
        {
            var security = _mapper.Map<Security>(securityDto);

            var userSecurity = await _securityService.GetSecurityUser(id);

            security.Id = userSecurity.Id;
            security.Password = _passwordService.Hash(security.Password);
            await _securityService.UpdateCredentials(security);

            var securityResult = _mapper.Map<SecurityDto>(security);
            var response = new ApiResponse<SecurityDto>(securityResult);
            return Ok(response);
        }

    }
}
---------------------------------------
TokenController.cs
************
﻿using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Cors;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.DataProtection;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc;
using Microsoft.Extensions.Configuration;
using Microsoft.IdentityModel.Tokens;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Infrastructure.Interfaces;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.IdentityModel.Tokens.Jwt;
using System.Security.Claims;
using System.Text;
using System.Threading.Tasks;
using TransforSerPu.Core.Dtos;
using TransforSerPu.Core.Interfaces;

namespace SocialMedia.Api.Controllers
{
    [Route("api/[Controller]")]
    [ApiController]
    [EnableCors("AllowAllOrigins")]
    public class TokenController : ControllerBase
    {
        private readonly IConfiguration _configuration;
        private readonly ISecurityService _securityService;
        private readonly IPasswordService _passwordService;
        private readonly ITokenService _tokenService;
        private readonly IRolModuleService _rolModuleService;
        private readonly IUserService _userService;


        private string issuer;
        private string audience;
        private string secret;

        public TokenController(IConfiguration configuration, ISecurityService securityService, IPasswordService passwordService, ITokenService tokenService, IRolModuleService rolModuleService, IUserService userService)
        {
            _configuration = configuration;
            _securityService = securityService;
            _passwordService = passwordService;
            _tokenService = tokenService;

            issuer = _configuration["Authentication:Issuer"];
            audience = _configuration["Authentication:Audience"];
            secret = _configuration["Authentication:SecretKey"];
            _rolModuleService = rolModuleService;
            _userService = userService;
        }

        [HttpPost]
        public async Task<IActionResult> GetToken(UserLoginDto login)
        {
            try
            {
                if (login is null)
                {
                    return BadRequest("Invalid client request");
                }

                //If valid user
                var result = await ValidateUser(login);

                if (!result.Item1)
                {
                    return Unauthorized();
                }

                var security = result.Item2;

                var claims = new List<Claim>
            {
                new Claim(ClaimTypes.Name, security.UserName),
                    new Claim(ClaimTypes.Role, security.Role.ToString()),
            };
                var accessToken = _tokenService.GenerateAccessToken(claims, issuer, audience, secret);
                var refreshToken = _tokenService.GenerateRefreshToken();

                await _securityService.UpdateRefreshToken(security.UserName, refreshToken);

                var permisos = _rolModuleService.ObtenerModulosUsuario(security.UserId);

                return Ok(new AuthenticatedResponse
                {
                    AuthToken = accessToken,
                    RefreshToken = refreshToken,
                    UserId = security.Id,
                    UserName = security.UserName,
                    Permisos = permisos
                });
            }
            catch (Exception ex)
            {
                return BadRequest(ex.Message);
            }
        }

        [HttpPost]
        [Route("RenewToken")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> RenewToken(TokenDto tokenApiModel)
        {
            if (tokenApiModel is null)
                return BadRequest("Invalid client request");

            var result = await this._tokenService.RenewToken(tokenApiModel);

            return Ok(result);
        }

        [HttpPost]
        [Route("revoke")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Revoke()
        {
            var username = User.Identity.Name;
            var user = await _securityService.GetLoginByCredentials(new UserLoginDto() { User = username });
            if (user == null) return BadRequest();

            await _securityService.UpdateRefreshToken(username, null);

            return NoContent();
        }

        private async Task<(bool, Security)> ValidateUser(UserLoginDto login)
        {
            var user = await _securityService.GetLoginByCredentials(login);

            var usuario = await this._userService.GetUser(user.UserId);

            if (usuario == null || usuario.IsActive)
                return (false, user);

            var isValid = _passwordService.Check(user.Password, login.Password);
            return (isValid, user);
        }

        private string GenerateToken(Security security)
        {
            //Header
            var symmetricSecurityKey = new SymmetricSecurityKey(Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(_configuration["Authentication:SecretKey"]));
            var signingCredentials = new SigningCredentials(symmetricSecurityKey, SecurityAlgorithms.HmacSha256);
            var header = new JwtHeader(signingCredentials);

            //Claims
            var claims = new[]
            {
                new Claim(ClaimTypes.Name, security.UserName),
                new Claim("User", security.UserName),
                new Claim(ClaimTypes.Role, security.Role.ToString()),
            };

            //Payload
            var payload = new JwtPayload
            (
                _configuration["Authentication:Issuer"],
                _configuration["Authentication:Audience"],
                claims,
                DateTime.Now,
                DateTime.Now.AddMinutes(1)
            );

            var token = new JwtSecurityToken(header, payload);

            return new JwtSecurityTokenHandler().WriteToken(token);
        }
    }
}

---------------------------------------
UserController.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using Azure;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc;
using Newtonsoft.Json;
using SocialMedia.Api.Responses;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Dtos;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using SocialMedia.Infrastructure.Interfaces;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Net;
using System.Threading.Tasks;
using System;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Cors;

namespace SocialMedia.Api.Controllers
{
    [ApiController]
    [Route("api/[controller]")]
    [EnableCors("AllowAllOrigins")]
    public class UserController : ControllerBase
    {
        private readonly IUserService _userService;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;
        private readonly IUriService _uriService;
        private readonly ISecurityService _securityService;
        private readonly IPasswordService _passwordService;

        public UserController(IUserService userService, IMapper mapper, IUriService uriService, ISecurityService securityService, IPasswordService passwordService)
        {
            _userService = userService;
            _mapper = mapper;
            _uriService = uriService;
            _securityService = securityService;
            _passwordService = passwordService;
        }

        [HttpGet(Name = nameof(GetUsers))]
        [ProducesResponseType((int)HttpStatusCode.OK, Type = typeof(ApiResponse<IEnumerable<UserDto>>))]
        [ProducesResponseType((int)HttpStatusCode.BadRequest)]
        public IActionResult GetUsers([FromQuery] UserQueryFilter filters)
        {
            
            var users = _userService.GetUsers(filters);
            var userDto = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<UserDto>>(users);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<UserDto>>(userDto);

            var metaData = new Metadata
            {
                TotalCount = users.TotalCount,
                PageSize = users.PageSize,
                CurrentPage = users.CurrentPage,
                TotalPages = users.TotalPages,
                HasNextPage = users.HasNextPage,
                HasPreviousPage = users.HasPreviousPage,
            };

            response.Meta = metaData;
            Response.Headers.Add("X-Pagination", JsonConvert.SerializeObject(metaData));

            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Get(Guid id)
        {
            var user = await _userService.GetUser(id);
            var userDto = _mapper.Map<UserDto>(user);

            var security = await _securityService.GetSecurityUser(id);
            if (security != null)
            {
                userDto.UserName = security.UserName;
            }

            var response = new ApiResponse<UserDto>(userDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPost]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Post(UserDto userDto)
        {
            var user = _mapper.Map<User>(userDto);

            await _userService.InsertUser(user);

            var credential = new Security()
            {
                UserId = user.Id,   
                Role = Core.Enumerations.RoleType.Consumer,
                UserName = userDto.UserName,
                Password = _passwordService.Hash(userDto.Password),
                RefreshTokenExpiryTime = DateTime.Now.AddHours(1),
            };

            await _securityService.RegisterUser(credential);

            userDto = _mapper.Map<UserDto>(user);

            var response = new ApiResponse<UserDto>(userDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPut("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Put(Guid id, UserDto userDto)
        {
            var user = _mapper.Map<User>(userDto);
            user.Id = id;

            await _userService.UpdateUser(user);

            return Ok();
        }

        [HttpDelete("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Delete(Guid id)
        {
            await _userService.DeleteUser(id);
            return Ok();
        }
    }
}

﻿using AutoMapper;
using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Cors;

using SocialMedia.Infrastructure.Interfaces;

using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Api.Controllers
{
    [ApiController]
    [Route("api/[controller]")]
    [EnableCors("AllowAllOrigins")]
    public class UserInRolesController : ControllerBase
    {
        private readonly IUserInRolesService _userInRolesService;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;
        private readonly IUriService _uriService;

        public UserInRolesController(IUserInRolesService userInRolesService, IMapper mapper, IUriService uriService)

            _mapper = mapper;
            _uriService = uriService;
        }

        [HttpGet]
        [Route("getAll")]
        public IActionResult getAll(Guid userId)
        {
            var barriosList = _userInRolesService.GetAll(userId);
            var barriosDto = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<UserInRolesDto>>(barriosList);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<UserInRolesDto>>(barriosDto);

            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet(Name = nameof(GetUserInRoles))]
        [ProducesResponseType((int)HttpStatusCode.OK, Type = typeof(ApiResponse<IEnumerable<UserInRolesDto>>))]
        [ProducesResponseType((int)HttpStatusCode.BadRequest)]
        public IActionResult GetUserInRoles([FromQuery] UserInRolesQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var userInRoles = _userInRolesService.GetUserInRoles(filters);
            var userInRolesDto = _mapper.Map<IEnumerable<UserInRolesDto>>(userInRoles);
            var response = new ApiResponse<IEnumerable<UserInRolesDto>>(userInRolesDto);

            var metaData = new Metadata
            {
                TotalCount = userInRoles.TotalCount,
                PageSize = userInRoles.PageSize,
                CurrentPage = userInRoles.CurrentPage,
                TotalPages = userInRoles.TotalPages,
                HasNextPage = userInRoles.HasNextPage,
                HasPreviousPage = userInRoles.HasPreviousPage,

            response.Meta = metaData;
            Response.Headers.Add("X-Pagination", JsonConvert.SerializeObject(metaData));

            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpGet("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Get(Guid id)
        {
            var userInRole = await _userInRolesService.GetUserInRole(id);
            var userInRoleDto = _mapper.Map<UserInRolesDto>(userInRole);
            var response = new ApiResponse<UserInRolesDto>(userInRoleDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPost]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Post(UserInRolesDto userInRolesDto)
        {
            var userInRole = _mapper.Map<UserInRoles>(userInRolesDto);

            await _userInRolesService.InsertUserInRole(userInRole);

            userInRolesDto = _mapper.Map<UserInRolesDto>(userInRole);

            var response = new ApiResponse<UserInRolesDto>(userInRolesDto);
            return Ok(response);
        }

        [HttpPut("{id}")]
        public async Task<IActionResult> Put(Guid id, UserInRolesDto userInRolesDto)
        {
            var userInRole = _mapper.Map<UserInRoles>(userInRolesDto);
            userInRole.Id = id;

            await _userInRolesService.UpdateUserInRole(userInRole);

            return Ok();
        }

        [HttpDelete("{id}")]

        {
            await _userInRolesService.DeleteUserInRole(id);
            return Ok();
        }
    }

}
