ClasificacionService.cs
************
﻿using Microsoft.Extensions.Options;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{
    public class ClasificacionService : IClasificacionService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;

        public ClasificacionService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
        }

        public IEnumerable<Clasificacion> GetAll()
        {
            var barrios = _unitOfWork.ClasificacionRepository.Get(x => x.Orden,
                x1 => x1.Familia, x2 => x2.Genero, x3 => x3.Especie);
            return barrios;
        }

        public async Task Insert(Clasificacion role)
        {
            // Additional business validations if necessary

            await _unitOfWork.ClasificacionRepository.Insert(role);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> Update(Clasificacion role)
        {
            var existing = await _unitOfWork.ClasificacionRepository.GetById(role.Id);
            if (existing == null)
                throw new BusinessException("Role doesn't exist");

            existing.EspecieId = role.EspecieId;
            existing.OrdenId = role.OrdenId;
            existing.FamiliaId = role.FamiliaId;
            existing.GeneroId = role.GeneroId;
            existing.NombreCientifico = role.NombreCientifico;
            existing.NombreComun = role.NombreComun;

            await _unitOfWork.ClasificacionRepository.Update(existing);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<Clasificacion> Get(Guid id)
        {
            return await _unitOfWork.ClasificacionRepository.GetById(id);
        }

        public PagedList<Clasificacion> Get(ClasificacionQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var Clasificacion = _unitOfWork
                .ClasificacionRepository.Get(x=> x.Genero,
                y=> y.Especie,
                w=> w.Familia);

            // Set default pagination values or use provided filters
            filters.PageNumber = filters.PageNumber;
            filters.PageSize = filters.PageSize;

            var pagedClasificacion = PagedList<Clasificacion>.Create(Clasificacion, filters.PageNumber, filters.PageSize);

            return pagedClasificacion;
        }

        public async Task Delete(Guid id)
        {
            await _unitOfWork.ClasificacionRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }
    }

}

---------------------------------------
CommentService.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using Microsoft.Extensions.Options;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using System;
using System.Linq;
using System.Threading.Tasks;


namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{
    public class CommentService : ICommentService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;

        public CommentService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions, IMapper mapper)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
        }

        public async Task InsertComment(Comment comment)
        {
            var user = await _unitOfWork.UserRepository.GetById(comment.UserId);
            if (user == null)
                throw new BusinessException("User doesn't exist");

            if (comment.Description.Contains("sexo"))
                throw new BusinessException("Content not allowed");

            // Additional business validations if necessary

            await _unitOfWork.CommentRepository.Insert(comment);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> UpdateComment(Comment comment)
        {
            var existingComment = await _unitOfWork.CommentRepository.GetById(comment.Id);
            if (existingComment == null)
                throw new BusinessException("Comment doesn't exist");

            existingComment.Description = comment.Description;
            existingComment.IsActive = comment.IsActive;


            await _unitOfWork.CommentRepository.Update(existingComment);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<Comment> GetComment(Guid id)
        {
            return await _unitOfWork.CommentRepository.GetById(id);
        }

        public PagedList<Comment> GetComments(CommentQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var comments = _unitOfWork.CommentRepository.Get();

            // Set default pagination values or use provided filters
            filters.PageNumber = filters.PageNumber;
            filters.PageSize = filters.PageSize;

            // Additional filtering logic if necessary
            Guid guidOutput;
            if (filters.Filter != null && Guid.TryParse(filters.Filter, out guidOutput))
            {
                comments = comments.Where(x => x.UserId == guidOutput);
            }

            if (filters.Filter != null)
            {
                comments = comments.Where(x => x.Description.Contains(filters.Filter));
            }

            var pagedComments = PagedList<Comment>.Create(comments, filters.PageNumber, filters.PageSize);

            return pagedComments;
        }

        public async Task DeleteComment(Guid id)
        {
            await _unitOfWork.CommentRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }
    }

}

---------------------------------------
ConsecutivoService.cs
************
﻿using Microsoft.Extensions.Options;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Linq;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{
    public class ConsecutivoService : IConsecutivoService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;

        public ConsecutivoService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
        }

        public IEnumerable<Consecutivo> GetAll()
        {
            var barrios = _unitOfWork.ConsecutivoRepository.Get();
            return barrios;
        }

        public async Task Insert(Consecutivo role)
        {
            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(role.Tabla))
                throw new BusinessException("Role name is required");

            // Additional business validations if necessary

            await _unitOfWork.ConsecutivoRepository.Insert(role);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> Update(Consecutivo role)
        {
            var existingRole = await _unitOfWork.ConsecutivoRepository.GetById(role.Id);
            if (existingRole == null)
                throw new BusinessException("Role doesn't exist");

            existingRole.Sufijo = role.Sufijo;
            existingRole.Prefijo = role.Prefijo;
            existingRole.UltimoConsecutivo = role.UltimoConsecutivo;
            existingRole.LongitudCodigo = role.LongitudCodigo;
            existingRole.Mascara = role.Mascara;

            await _unitOfWork.ConsecutivoRepository.Update(existingRole);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<Consecutivo> Get(Guid id)
        {
            return await _unitOfWork.ConsecutivoRepository.GetById(id);
        }



        public async Task Delete(Guid id)
        {
            await _unitOfWork.ConsecutivoRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        // Método para obtener el siguiente consecutivo de manera atómica
        public string ObtenerSiguienteConsecutivo(string nombreTabla)
        {
            // Obtener el consecutivo actual de la tabla
            var consecutivo = _unitOfWork.ConsecutivoRepository
                                          .Get(x => x.Tabla == nombreTabla)
                                          .SingleOrDefault();

            if (consecutivo == null)
            {
                throw new Exception("No se encontró un consecutivo para la tabla especificada.");
            }

            // Incrementar el último consecutivo
            consecutivo.UltimoConsecutivo++;

            // Generar el nuevo código con el prefijo, sufijo y máscara si es necesario
            string nuevoCodigo = GenerarCodigoConsecutivo(consecutivo);

            // Guardar el cambio en el consecutivo
            _unitOfWork.ConsecutivoRepository.Update(consecutivo);

            return nuevoCodigo;
        }

        // Método para generar el código consecutivo basado en la configuración del consecutivo
        private string GenerarCodigoConsecutivo(Consecutivo consecutivo)
        {
            var codigoBase = string.Empty;
            // Rellenar con la máscara si es necesario
            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(consecutivo.Mascara))
            {
                codigoBase = aplicarMascara(consecutivo.UltimoConsecutivo.ToString(), consecutivo.Mascara, consecutivo.LongitudCodigo);
            }

            return $"{consecutivo.Prefijo}{codigoBase}{consecutivo.Sufijo}";
        }

        // Método para aplicar una máscara al código, asumiendo que la máscara es un string como "00000"
        private string aplicarMascara(string codigo, string mascara, int longitudCodigo)
        {
            return codigo.PadLeft(longitudCodigo, mascara[0]);
        }
    }

}

---------------------------------------
DetalleService.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using Microsoft.Extensions.Options;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Linq;
using System.Text;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{
    public class DetalleService : IDetalleService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;

        public DetalleService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions, IMapper mapper)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
            _mapper = mapper;
        }

        public async Task InsertDetalle(Detalle detalle)
        {
            // Lógica para insertar un nuevo censo arbóreo.
            await _unitOfWork.DetalleRepository.Insert(detalle);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> UpdateDetalle(Detalle detalle)
        {
            var existingDetalle = await _unitOfWork.DetalleRepository.GetById(detalle.Id);
            if (existingDetalle == null)
                throw new BusinessException("Detalle doesn't exist");

            existingDetalle.Descripcion = detalle.Descripcion;
            existingDetalle.Nombre = detalle.Nombre;
            existingDetalle.Codigo = detalle.Codigo;
            existingDetalle.MaestraId = detalle.MaestraId;


            // Lógica para actualizar un censo arbóreo existente.
            await _unitOfWork.DetalleRepository.Update(existingDetalle);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<Detalle> GetDetalle(Guid id)
        {
            // Lógica para obtener un censo arbóreo por su ID.
            return await _unitOfWork.DetalleRepository.GetById(id);
        }

        public async Task<List<Detalle>> GetDetallesByMaestra(Guid id)
        {
            var detalles = _unitOfWork.DetalleRepository.Get();
            detalles = detalles.Where(x => x.MaestraId.Equals(id));
            return detalles.ToList<Detalle>();
        }


        public PagedList<Detalle> GetDetalles(DetalleQueryFilter filters)
        {
            
            var detalles = _unitOfWork.DetalleRepository.Get();


            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(filters.Filter))
            {
                filters.Filter = filters.Filter.ToUpper().Replace(" ", "");
            }
                detalles = detalles.Where(x =>

                    
                    (((filters.IdMaestra =="0") || x.MaestraId == new Guid(filters.IdMaestra) ) &&


                    (string.IsNullOrEmpty(filters.Filter) ||
                    (x.Nombre.ToUpper().Replace(" ", "").Contains(filters.Filter) ||
                    x.Codigo.ToUpper().Replace(" ", "").Contains(filters.Filter) ||
                    x.Descripcion.ToUpper().Replace(" ", "").Contains(filters.Filter))
                    ))
                    
                    
                    );
            
            // Aplicar filtros según las necesidades de tu aplicación.
            var pagedCensos = PagedList<Detalle>.Create(detalles, filters.PageNumber, filters.PageSize);
            return pagedCensos;
        }

        public async Task DeleteDetalle(Guid id)
        {
            // Lógica para eliminar un censo arbóreo por su ID.
            await _unitOfWork.DetalleRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }
    }


    

}

---------------------------------------
EspaciosPotencialesService.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using Microsoft.Extensions.Options;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Dtos;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Linq;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{
    public class EspaciosPotencialesService : IEspaciosPotencialesService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;

        public EspaciosPotencialesService(
            IUnitOfWork unitOfWork,
            IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions,
            IMapper mapper
        )
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
            _mapper = mapper;
        }

        public async Task InsertEspaciosPotenciales(EspaciosPotenciales espaciosPotenciales)
        {
            await _unitOfWork.EspaciosPotencialesRepository.Insert(espaciosPotenciales);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> UpdateEspaciosPotenciales(EspaciosPotenciales espaciosPotenciales)
        {
            
            var fotosNuevas = espaciosPotenciales.Fotos.Where(x => x.Id == Guid.Empty).ToList();
            var fotosActuales = espaciosPotenciales.Fotos.Where(x => x.Id != Guid.Empty).ToList();

            var existingEspaciosPotenciales =
                await _unitOfWork.EspaciosPotencialesRepository.GetById(espaciosPotenciales.Id, i=> i.Coordenada);
            if (existingEspaciosPotenciales == null)
                throw new BusinessException("EspaciosPotenciales doesn't exist");

            existingEspaciosPotenciales.AreasDisponibles = espaciosPotenciales.AreasDisponibles;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.TipoEmplazamiento = espaciosPotenciales.TipoEmplazamiento;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.EspeciesPotencialesParaSiembraAlMenosTresOpciones =
                espaciosPotenciales.EspeciesPotencialesParaSiembraAlMenosTresOpciones;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.AlturasPotencialesArboles =
                espaciosPotenciales.AlturasPotencialesArboles;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.CaracteristicasEdaficasODelSuelo =
                espaciosPotenciales.CaracteristicasEdaficasODelSuelo;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.TresBolillo = espaciosPotenciales.TresBolillo;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.Cuadrado = espaciosPotenciales.Cuadrado;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.Rectangular = espaciosPotenciales.Rectangular;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.IndividualOUno = espaciosPotenciales.IndividualOUno;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.DistanciamientoSiembra =
                espaciosPotenciales.DistanciamientoSiembra;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.InfraestructuraAfectada =
                espaciosPotenciales.InfraestructuraAfectada;

            existingEspaciosPotenciales.PendienteDelTerreno =
                espaciosPotenciales.PendienteDelTerreno;
            
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.Barrio = espaciosPotenciales.Barrio;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.Comuna = espaciosPotenciales.Comuna;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.AltitudASNM = espaciosPotenciales.AltitudASNM;

            

            existingEspaciosPotenciales.Coordenada.Latitud = espaciosPotenciales.Coordenada.Latitud;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.Coordenada.Longitud = espaciosPotenciales.Coordenada.Longitud;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.Coordenada.Altitud = espaciosPotenciales.Coordenada.Altitud;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.Coordenada.Norte = espaciosPotenciales.Coordenada.Norte;
            existingEspaciosPotenciales.Coordenada.Este = espaciosPotenciales.Coordenada.Este;



            existingEspaciosPotenciales.Fotos = existingEspaciosPotenciales.Fotos.Where(x => fotosActuales.Any(p => p.Id == x.Id)).ToList();

            await _unitOfWork.EspaciosPotencialesRepository.Update(existingEspaciosPotenciales);


            
            foreach (var fn in fotosNuevas)
            {

                var nueva = new RegistroFotograficoEspacio()
                {
                    Nombre = fn.Nombre,
                    Url = fn.Url,
                    EspaciosPotencialesId = existingEspaciosPotenciales.Id,
                };

                var nuevaEntity = await _unitOfWork.RegistroFotograficoEspacioPotencialRepository.Insert(nueva);
            }

            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<EspaciosPotenciales> GetEspaciosPotenciales(Guid id)
        {
            return await _unitOfWork.EspaciosPotencialesRepository.GetById(
                id, i => i.Coordenada);
        }

        public PagedList<EspaciosPotenciales> GetEspaciosPotenciales(
            EspaciosPotencialesQueryFilter filters
        )
        {
            var espacios = _unitOfWork.EspaciosPotencialesRepository.Get();

            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(filters.Filter))
            {
                espacios = espacios.Where(
                    x =>
                        x.TipoEmplazamiento.Contains(filters.Filter)
                        || x.EspeciesPotencialesParaSiembraAlMenosTresOpciones.Contains(
                            filters.Filter
                        )
                        || x.InfraestructuraAfectada.Contains(filters.Filter)
                        || x.PendienteDelTerreno.Contains(filters.Filter)
                        || x.Barrio.Contains(filters.Filter)
                        || x.Comuna.Contains(filters.Filter)
                );
            }

            var pagedEspacios = PagedList<EspaciosPotenciales>.Create(
                espacios,
                filters.PageNumber,
                filters.PageSize
            );
            return pagedEspacios;
        }

        public async Task DeleteEspaciosPotenciales(Guid id)
        {
            await _unitOfWork.EspaciosPotencialesRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<IEnumerable<EspaciosPotencialesCSV>> ExportEspaciosPotencialesData() {

            var items = this._unitOfWork.EspaciosPotencialesRepository.Get(x => x.Coordenada).ToList();
            return items.Select(x => new EspaciosPotencialesCSV() {
                AreasDisponibles = x.AreasDisponibles,
                TipoEmplazamiento = x.TipoEmplazamiento,
                EspeciesPotencialesParaSiembraAlMenosTresOpciones = x.EspeciesPotencialesParaSiembraAlMenosTresOpciones,
                AlturasPotencialesArboles = x.AlturasPotencialesArboles,
                CaracteristicasEdaficasODelSuelo = x.CaracteristicasEdaficasODelSuelo,
                TresBolillo = x.TresBolillo,
                Cuadrado = x.Cuadrado,
                Rectangular = x.Rectangular,
                IndividualOUno = x.IndividualOUno,
                DistanciamientoSiembra = x.DistanciamientoSiembra,
                InfraestructuraAfectada = x.InfraestructuraAfectada,
                PendienteDelTerreno = x.PendienteDelTerreno,
                Barrio = x.Barrio,
                Comuna = x.Comuna,
                AltitudASNM = x.AltitudASNM,

                Altitud = x.Coordenada?.Altitud,
                Latitud = x.Coordenada?.Latitud,
                Longitud = x.Coordenada?.Longitud,
                Este = x.Coordenada?.Este,
                Norte = x.Coordenada?.Norte

            });
        }

        public async Task CargarArchivoEspaciosPotenciales(List<EspaciosPotencialesCSV> request)
        {
            // Aquí se asume que hay algún tipo de validación o procesamiento previo
            // para asegurarse de que los datos son correctos antes de insertarlos en la base de datos.

            var espaciosPotencialesParaInsertar = request.Select(x => new EspaciosPotenciales
            {
                AreasDisponibles = x.AreasDisponibles,
                TipoEmplazamiento = x.TipoEmplazamiento,
                EspeciesPotencialesParaSiembraAlMenosTresOpciones = x.EspeciesPotencialesParaSiembraAlMenosTresOpciones,
                AlturasPotencialesArboles = x.AlturasPotencialesArboles,
                CaracteristicasEdaficasODelSuelo = x.CaracteristicasEdaficasODelSuelo,
                TresBolillo = x.TresBolillo,
                Cuadrado = x.Cuadrado,
                Rectangular = x.Rectangular,
                IndividualOUno = x.IndividualOUno,
                DistanciamientoSiembra = x.DistanciamientoSiembra,
                InfraestructuraAfectada = x.InfraestructuraAfectada,
                PendienteDelTerreno = x.PendienteDelTerreno,
                Barrio = x.Barrio,
                Comuna = x.Comuna,
                AltitudASNM = x.AltitudASNM,
                Coordenada = new Coordenada // Asumiendo que hay un tipo Coordenada que maneja estas propiedades
                {
                    Latitud = x.Latitud,
                    Longitud = x.Longitud,
                    Altitud = x.Altitud,
                    Norte = x.Norte,
                    Este = x.Este
                }
            }).ToList();

            // Insertar los nuevos registros de espacios potenciales en la base de datos
            var resultado = await this._unitOfWork.EspaciosPotencialesRepository.Insert(espaciosPotencialesParaInsertar);

            // Puedes manejar el resultado de la inserción según sea necesario,
            // por ejemplo, verificar si se han insertado correctamente los registros,
            // o manejar cualquier error que haya ocurrido.
        }
    }
}

MaestraService.cs
************
﻿using AutoMapper;
using Microsoft.Extensions.DependencyInjection;
using Microsoft.Extensions.Options;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Linq;
using System.Text;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{
    public class MaestraService : IMaestraService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;

        public MaestraService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions, IMapper mapper)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
            _mapper = mapper;
        }

        public async Task InsertMaestra(Maestra maestra)
        {
            // Lógica para insertar un nuevo censo arbóreo.
            await _unitOfWork.MaestraRepository.Insert(maestra);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> UpdateMaestra(Maestra maestra)
        {
            var existingMaestra = await _unitOfWork.MaestraRepository.GetById(maestra.Id);
            if (existingMaestra == null)
                throw new BusinessException("Maestra doesn't exist");

            existingMaestra.NombreTabla = maestra.NombreTabla;
            

            // Lógica para actualizar un censo arbóreo existente.
            await _unitOfWork.MaestraRepository.Update(existingMaestra);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<Maestra> GetMaestra(Guid id)
        {
            // Lógica para obtener un censo arbóreo por su ID.
            return await _unitOfWork.MaestraRepository.GetById(id);
        }

        public PagedList<Maestra> GetMaestras(MaestraQueryFilter filters)
        {
            
            var maestras = _unitOfWork.MaestraRepository.Get();            

            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(filters.Filter))
            {
                maestras = maestras.Where(x =>
                    x.NombreTabla.Contains(filters.Filter));
                    
            }

            var pagedCensos = PagedList<Maestra>.Create(maestras, filters.PageNumber, filters.PageSize);
            return pagedCensos;
        }

        public async Task DeleteMaestra(Guid id)
        {
            // Lógica para eliminar un censo arbóreo por su ID.
            await _unitOfWork.MaestraRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public Task<List<Maestra>> GetAll()
        {
            var a = _unitOfWork.MaestraRepository.GetByAll().ToList();            
            return Task.FromResult(a);
        }
    }


    public class OrdenService : IOrdenService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;

        public OrdenService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions, IMapper mapper)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
            _mapper = mapper;
        }

        public async Task Insert(object entity)
        {
            var orden = entity as Orden;
            // Lógica para insertar un nuevo censo arbóreo.
            await _unitOfWork.OrdenRepository.Insert(orden);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> Update(object entity, Guid id)
        {
            var orden = entity as Orden;
            orden.Id = id;
            var existing = await _unitOfWork.OrdenRepository.GetById(orden.Id);
            if (existing == null)
                throw new BusinessException("Orden doesn't exist");

            existing.Descripcion = orden.Descripcion;


            // Lógica para actualizar un censo arbóreo existente.
            await _unitOfWork.OrdenRepository.Update(existing);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<object> Get(Guid id)
        {
            // Lógica para obtener un censo arbóreo por su ID.
            return await _unitOfWork.OrdenRepository.GetById(id);
        }

       

        public PagedList<object> Get(BasicTableQueryFilter filters)
        {

            var entities = _unitOfWork.OrdenRepository.Get();

            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(filters.Filter))
            {
                entities = entities.Where(x =>
                    x.Descripcion.Contains(filters.Filter));

            }

            var pagedCensos = PagedList<object>.Create(entities, filters.PageNumber, filters.PageSize);
            return pagedCensos;
        }

        public async Task Delete(Guid id)
        {
            // Lógica para eliminar un censo arbóreo por su ID.
            await _unitOfWork.OrdenRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        

        Task<List<object>> IBasicTableService.GetAll()
        {
            var a = _unitOfWork.OrdenRepository.GetByAll().ToList();
            var b = new List<object>();
            foreach (var entity in a)
            {
                b.Add(entity);
            }
            return Task.FromResult(b);
        }



        public Task<List<object>> GetByPredecesor(Guid id)
        {
            var entities = _unitOfWork.OrdenRepository.Get();            
            var b = entities.Select(x => (object)x).ToList();
            return Task.FromResult(b);
        }
    }

        }

        public Task<List<object>> GetByPredecesor(Guid id)
        {

            var b = entities.Select(x => (object)x).ToList();
            return Task.FromResult(b);
        }
    }

    public class GeneroService : IGeneroService
    {

    public class EspecieService : IEspecieService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;

        public EspecieService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions, IMapper mapper)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
            _mapper = mapper;
        }

        public async Task Insert(object entity)
        {
            var especie = entity as Especie;
            await _unitOfWork.EspecieRepository.Insert(especie);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> Update(object entity, Guid id)
        {
            var especie = entity as Especie;
            especie.Id = id;
            var existing = await _unitOfWork.EspecieRepository.GetById(especie.Id);
            if (existing == null)
                throw new BusinessException("Especie doesn't exist");

            existing.Descripcion = especie.Descripcion;
            existing.GeneroId = especie.GeneroId;

            // Lógica para actualizar un censo arbóreo existente.
            await _unitOfWork.EspecieRepository.Update(existing);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<object> Get(Guid id)
        {
            // Lógica para obtener un censo arbóreo por su ID.
            return await _unitOfWork.EspecieRepository.GetById(id, i=>i.Genero);
        }

      

        public PagedList<object> Get(BasicTableQueryFilter filters)
        {

            var entities = _unitOfWork.EspecieRepository.Get(i=>i.Genero);

            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(filters.Filter))
            {
                entities = entities.Where(x =>
                    x.Descripcion.Contains(filters.Filter));

            }

            var pagedCensos = PagedList<object>.Create(entities, filters.PageNumber, filters.PageSize);
            return pagedCensos;
        }

        public async Task Delete(Guid id)
        {
            // Lógica para eliminar un censo arbóreo por su ID.
            await _unitOfWork.EspecieRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }
        Task<List<object>> IBasicTableService.GetAll()
        {
            var a = _unitOfWork.EspecieRepository.GetByAll().ToList();
            var b = new List<object>();
            foreach (var entity in a)
            {
                b.Add(entity);
            }
            return Task.FromResult(b);
        }
        public Task<List<object>> GetByPredecesor(Guid id)
        {
            var entities = _unitOfWork.EspecieRepository.Get().Where(x => x.GeneroId == id);
            var b = entities.Select(x => (object)x).ToList();
            return Task.FromResult(b);
        }
    }


    public class ComunaService : IComunaService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;

        public ComunaService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions, IMapper mapper)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
            _mapper = mapper;
        }

        public async Task Insert(object entity)
        {
            var orden = entity as Comuna;
            // Lógica para insertar un nuevo censo arbóreo.
            await _unitOfWork.ComunaRepository.Insert(orden);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> Update(object entity, Guid id)
        {
            var orden = entity as Comuna;
            orden.Id = id;
            var existing = await _unitOfWork.ComunaRepository.GetById(orden.Id);
            if (existing == null)
                throw new BusinessException("Comuna doesn't exist");

            existing.Descripcion = orden.Descripcion;


            // Lógica para actualizar un censo arbóreo existente.
            await _unitOfWork.ComunaRepository.Update(existing);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<object> Get(Guid id)
        {
            // Lógica para obtener un censo arbóreo por su ID.
            return await _unitOfWork.ComunaRepository.GetById(id);
        }



        public PagedList<object> Get(BasicTableQueryFilter filters)
        {

            var entities = _unitOfWork.ComunaRepository.Get();

            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(filters.Filter))
            {
                entities = entities.Where(x =>
                    x.Descripcion.ToUpper().Replace(" ", "").Contains(filters.Filter.ToUpper().Replace(" ",""))); 

            }

            var pagedCensos = PagedList<object>.Create(entities, filters.PageNumber, filters.PageSize);
            return pagedCensos;
        }

        public async Task Delete(Guid id)
        {
            // Lógica para eliminar un censo arbóreo por su ID.
            await _unitOfWork.ComunaRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }



        Task<List<object>> IBasicTableService.GetAll()
        {
            var a = _unitOfWork.ComunaRepository.GetByAll().ToList();
            var b = new List<object>();
            foreach (var entity in a)
            {
                b.Add(entity);
            }
            return Task.FromResult(b);
        }

        public Task<List<object>> GetByPredecesor(Guid id)
        {
            var entities = _unitOfWork.ComunaRepository.Get();            
            var b = entities.Select(x => (object)x).ToList();
            return Task.FromResult(b);
        }
    }

    public class BarrioService : IBarrioService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;
        private readonly IMapper _mapper;

        public BarrioService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions, IMapper mapper)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
            _mapper = mapper;
        }

        public async Task Insert(object entity)
        {
            var familia = entity as Barrio;
            await _unitOfWork.BarrioRepository.Insert(familia);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> Update(object entity, Guid id)
        {
            var familia = entity as Barrio;
            familia.Id = id;
            var existing = await _unitOfWork.BarrioRepository.GetById(familia.Id);
            if (existing == null)
                throw new BusinessException("Barrio doesn't exist");

            existing.Descripcion = familia.Descripcion;
            existing.ComunaId = familia.ComunaId;


            // Lógica para actualizar un censo arbóreo existente.
            await _unitOfWork.BarrioRepository.Update(existing);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<object> Get(Guid id)
        {
            // Lógica para obtener un censo arbóreo por su ID.
            return await _unitOfWork.BarrioRepository.GetById(id, i => i.Comuna);
        }

        public PagedList<object> Get(BasicTableQueryFilter filters)
        {

            var entities = _unitOfWork.BarrioRepository.Get(i => i.Comuna);

            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(filters.Filter))
            {
                entities = entities.Where(x =>
                    x.Descripcion.ToUpper().Replace(" ", "").Contains(filters.Filter.ToUpper().Replace(" ", "")) || 
                    x.Comuna.Descripcion.ToUpper().Replace(" ", "").Contains(filters.Filter.ToUpper().Replace(" ", ""))
                    );

            }

            var pagedCensos = PagedList<object>.Create(entities, filters.PageNumber, filters.PageSize);
            return pagedCensos;
        }

        public async Task Delete(Guid id)
        {
            // Lógica para eliminar un censo arbóreo por su ID.
            await _unitOfWork.BarrioRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }
        Task<List<object>> IBasicTableService.GetAll()
        {
            var a = _unitOfWork.BarrioRepository.GetByAll().ToList();
            var b = new List<object>();
            foreach (var entity in a)
            {
                b.Add(entity);
            }
            return Task.FromResult(b);
        }

        public Task<List<object>> GetByPredecesor(Guid id)
        {
            var entities = _unitOfWork.BarrioRepository.Get().Where(x => x.ComunaId == id);
            var b = entities.ToList().Select(x => (object)x).ToList();
            return Task.FromResult(b);
        }
    }





}

ModuleService.cs
************
﻿using Microsoft.Extensions.Options;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Linq;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{
    public class ModuleService : IModuleService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;

        public ModuleService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
        }

        public IEnumerable<Modules> GetAll()
        {
            var barrios = _unitOfWork.ModuleRepository.Get();
            return barrios;
        }


        public async Task Insert(Modules input)
        {
            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(input.ModuleName))
                throw new BusinessException("Role name is required");

            // Additional business validations if necessary

            await _unitOfWork.ModuleRepository.Insert(input);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> Update(Modules role)
        {
            var existingRole = await _unitOfWork.ModuleRepository.GetById(role.Id);
            if (existingRole == null)
                throw new BusinessException("Role doesn't exist");

            existingRole.ModuleName = role.ModuleName;

            await _unitOfWork.ModuleRepository.Update(existingRole);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<Modules> Get(Guid id)
        {
            return await _unitOfWork.ModuleRepository.GetById(id);
        }

        public PagedList<Modules> Get(ModulesQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var Module = _unitOfWork.ModuleRepository.Get();

            // Set default pagination values or use provided filters
            filters.PageNumber = filters.PageNumber;
            filters.PageSize = filters.PageSize;

            // Additional filtering logic if necessary
            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(filters.Filter))
            {
                Module = Module.Where(x => x.ModuleName.ToLower()
                .Contains(filters.Filter.ToLower()));
            }

            var pagedModule = PagedList<Modules>.Create(Module, filters.PageNumber, filters.PageSize);

            return pagedModule;
        }

        public async Task Delete(Guid id)
        {
            await _unitOfWork.ModuleRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }
    }

}

PasswordRecoveryService.cs
************
﻿using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using System;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{
    public class PasswordRecoveryService : IPasswordRecoveryService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        // Consider adding more dependencies if necessary, like sending emails

        public PasswordRecoveryService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
        }

        public async Task InsertRecovery(PasswordRecovery recovery)
        {
            var user = await _unitOfWork.UserRepository.GetById(recovery.UserId);
            if (user == null)
                throw new BusinessException("User doesn't exist");

            // Add additional business validations if necessary

            await _unitOfWork.PasswordRecoveryRepository.Insert(recovery);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> UpdateRecovery(PasswordRecovery recovery)
        {
            var existingRecovery = await _unitOfWork.PasswordRecoveryRepository.GetById(recovery.PasswordRecoveryToken);
            if (existingRecovery == null)
                throw new BusinessException("Recovery Token doesn't exist");

            existingRecovery.ExpiryDate = recovery.ExpiryDate;

            await _unitOfWork.PasswordRecoveryRepository.Update(existingRecovery);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<PasswordRecovery> GetRecovery(Guid token)
        {
            return await _unitOfWork.PasswordRecoveryRepository.GetById(token);
        }

        public async Task DeleteRecovery(Guid token)
        {
            await _unitOfWork.PasswordRecoveryRepository.Delete(token);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }
    }

}

---------------------------------------
PostService.cs
************
﻿using Microsoft.Extensions.Options;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using System;
using System.Linq;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{

    public class PostService : IPostService
    {

        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;
        public PostService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
        }

        public async Task InsertPost(Post post)
        {
            var user = await _unitOfWork.UserRepository.GetById(post.UserId);
            if (user == null)
                throw new BusinessException("User doesnt exist");

            if (post.Description.Contains("sexo"))
                throw new BusinessException("Content not allowed");

            var userPosts = await _unitOfWork.PostRepository.GetPostsByUser(post.UserId);
            if (userPosts.Count() < 10)
            {
                var lastPost = userPosts.OrderByDescending(x => x.Date).FirstOrDefault();
                if (lastPost != null && (System.DateTime.Now - lastPost.Date).TotalDays < 7)
                {
                    throw new BusinessException("you cant push any posts jet.");
                }
            }

            await _unitOfWork.PostRepository.Insert(post);
        }

        public async Task<bool> UpdatePost(Post post)
        {
            var existingPost = await _unitOfWork.PostRepository.GetById(post.Id, u => u.User);
            existingPost.Image = post.Image;
            existingPost.Description = post.Description;

            await _unitOfWork.PostRepository.Update(existingPost);
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<Post> GetPost(Guid id)
        {
            return await _unitOfWork.PostRepository.GetById(id, u => u.User);
        }

        public PagedList<Post> GetPosts(PostQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var posts = _unitOfWork.PostRepository.Get(u => u.User);

            filters.PageNumber = _paginationOptions.DefaultPageNumber;
            filters.PageSize = _paginationOptions.DefaultPageSize;

            Guid guidOutput;
            if (filters.Filter != null && Guid.TryParse(filters.Filter, out guidOutput))
            {
                posts = posts.Where(x => x.UserId == guidOutput);
            }

            /*if (filters.Filter != null)
            {
                posts = posts.Where(x => x.Date.ToShortDateString() == ((DateTime)filters.Date).ToShortDateString());
            }*/

            if (filters.Filter != null)
            {
                posts = posts.Where(x => x.Description.ToLower().Contains(filters.Filter.ToLower()));
            }

            var pagedPosts = PagedList<Post>.Create(posts, filters.PageSize, filters.PageSize);

            return pagedPosts;
        }

        public async Task DeletePost(Guid id)
        {
            await _unitOfWork.PostRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }
    }

}

RolesService.cs
************
﻿using Microsoft.Extensions.Options;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Linq;
using System.Text;
using System.Threading;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{
    public class RolesService : IRolesService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;

        public RolesService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
        }

        public IEnumerable<Roles> GetAll()
        {
            var barrios = _unitOfWork.RolesRepository.Get();
            return barrios;
        }

        public async Task Insert(Roles role)
        {
            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(role.RolName))
                throw new BusinessException("Role name is required");

            // Additional business validations if necessary

            await _unitOfWork.RolesRepository.Insert(role);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> Update(Roles role)
        {
            var existingRole = await _unitOfWork.RolesRepository.GetById(role.Id);
            if (existingRole == null)
                throw new BusinessException("Role doesn't exist");

            existingRole.RolName = role.RolName;

            await _unitOfWork.RolesRepository.Update(existingRole);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<Roles> Get(Guid id)
        {
            return await _unitOfWork.RolesRepository.GetById(id);
        }

        public PagedList<Roles> Get(RolesQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var roles = _unitOfWork.RolesRepository.Get();

            // Set default pagination values or use provided filters
            filters.PageNumber = filters.PageNumber;
            filters.PageSize = filters.PageSize;

            // Additional filtering logic if necessary
            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(filters.Filter))
            {
                roles = roles.Where(x => x.RolName.Contains(filters.Filter));
            }

            var pagedRoles = PagedList<Roles>.Create(roles, filters.PageNumber, filters.PageSize);

            return pagedRoles;
        }

        public async Task Delete(Guid id)
        {
            await _unitOfWork.RolesRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }
    }

}

---------------------------------------
RolModuleService.cs
************
﻿using Microsoft.Extensions.Options;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Dtos;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Linq;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{
    public class RolModuleService : IRolModuleService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;

        public RolModuleService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
        }

        public async Task InsertRolModule(RolModule rolModule)
        {
            var role = await _unitOfWork.RolesRepository.GetById(rolModule.IdRol);
            if (role == null)
                throw new BusinessException("Role doesn't exist");

            // Additional business validations if necessary

            await _unitOfWork.RolModuleRepository.Insert(rolModule);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> UpdateRolModule(RolModule rolModule)
        {
            var existingRolModule = await _unitOfWork.RolModuleRepository.GetById(rolModule.Id);
            if (existingRolModule == null)
                throw new BusinessException("RolModule doesn't exist");

            // Complete properties mapping
            existingRolModule.Module = rolModule.Module;
            existingRolModule.Created = rolModule.Created;
            existingRolModule.Edited = rolModule.Edited;
            existingRolModule.Listed = rolModule.Listed;
            existingRolModule.Deleted = rolModule.Deleted;
            existingRolModule.Printed = rolModule.Printed;
            existingRolModule.IdRol = rolModule.IdRol;

            await _unitOfWork.RolModuleRepository.Update(existingRolModule);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<RolModule> GetRolModule(Guid id)
        {
            return await _unitOfWork.RolModuleRepository.GetById(id);
        }

        public PagedList<RolModule> GetRolModules(RolModuleQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var rolModules = _unitOfWork.RolModuleRepository.Get(x => x.Module, y => y.Rol);

            // Using provided filters directly
            filters.PageNumber = filters.PageNumber;
            filters.PageSize = filters.PageSize;

            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(filters.Filter))
            {
                filters.Filter = filters.Filter.ToLower();

                rolModules = rolModules.Where(
                              x =>
                                  x.Rol.RolName.ToLower().Contains(filters.Filter)
                                  || x.Module.ModuleName.ToLower().Contains(filters.Filter));
            }
            var pagedRolModules = PagedList<RolModule>.Create(rolModules, filters.PageNumber, filters.PageSize);

            return pagedRolModules;
        }


        public async Task DeleteRolModule(Guid id)
        {
            await _unitOfWork.RolModuleRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public IEnumerable<RolModuleCombinadoDto> ObtenerModulosUsuario(Guid userId)
        {
            var listaRoles = this._unitOfWork.UserInRolesRepository
                .Get().Where(x => x.UserId == userId).Select(x => x.RolId).ToList();

            //Si contiene el rol administrador, responde full permisos a todos los modulos.
            if (listaRoles.Contains(Guid.Parse("6acb97ed-8141-47e5-bb5b-d89883d1e6dc")))
            {
                return this._unitOfWork.ModuleRepository.Get()
                .Select(x => new RolModuleCombinadoDto()
                {
                    Module = x.ModuleName,
                    Created = true,
                    Deleted = true,
                    Edited = true,
                    Listed = true,
                    Printed = true
                }).ToList();
            }

            var rolesModules = this._unitOfWork.RolModuleRepository.Get(x => x.Module, y => y.Rol)
                .Where(x => listaRoles.Contains(x.IdRol)).ToList();

            var combinedPermissions = CombineRolesPermissions(rolesModules)
                .Select(x => new RolModuleCombinadoDto()
                {
                    Module = x.Module.ModuleName,
                    Created = x.Created,
                    Deleted = x.Deleted,
                    Edited = x.Edited,
                    Listed = x.Listed,
                    Printed = x.Printed,
                }).ToList();

            return combinedPermissions;
        }

        private RolModule MergePermissions(RolModule perm1, RolModule perm2)
        {
            return new RolModule
            {
                Module = perm1.Module,
                Created = perm1.Created || perm2.Created,
                Edited = perm1.Edited || perm2.Edited,
                Listed = perm1.Listed || perm2.Listed,
                Deleted = perm1.Deleted || perm2.Deleted,
                Printed = perm1.Printed || perm2.Printed
            };
        }

        public IEnumerable<RolModule> CombineRolesPermissions(List<RolModule> rolesModules)
        {
            return rolesModules
                .GroupBy(rm => rm.Module) // Agrupar por módulo
                .Select(group => group.Aggregate((merged, next) => MergePermissions(merged, next))) // Combina los permisos
                .ToList();
        }
    }

}

---------------------------------------
SecurityService.cs
************
﻿using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using System;
using System.Linq;
using System.Text.Json;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{
    public class SecurityService : ISecurityService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;

        public SecurityService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
        }

        public async Task<Security> GetLoginByCredentials(UserLoginDto userLogin)
        {
            return await _unitOfWork.SecurityRepository.GetLoginByCredentials(userLogin);
        }

        public async Task RegisterUser(Security security)
        {
            await _unitOfWork.SecurityRepository.Add(security);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task UpdateRefreshToken(string userName, string refreshToken)
        {
            var sec = _unitOfWork.SecurityRepository
                .Get().Where(x => x.UserName == userName).FirstOrDefault();

            sec.RefreshToken = refreshToken;
            sec.RefreshTokenExpiryTime = DateTime.Now.AddDays(7);

            await _unitOfWork.SecurityRepository.Update(sec);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }


        public async Task UpdateCredentials(Security data)
        {
            var sec = await _unitOfWork.SecurityRepository.GetById(data.Id);

            sec.UserName = data.UserName;
            sec.Role = data.Role;
            sec.Password = data.Password;

            await _unitOfWork.SecurityRepository.Update(sec);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<Security> GetSecurityUser(Guid idUsuario)
        {

            var listSecurity = _unitOfWork.SecurityRepository.Get(x => x.User)
                .Where(x => x.UserId == idUsuario).FirstOrDefault();

            return listSecurity;
        }
    }
}
---------------------------------------
TokenService.cs
************
﻿using Microsoft.Extensions.Configuration;
using Microsoft.Extensions.Options;
using Microsoft.IdentityModel.Tokens;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.IdentityModel.Tokens.Jwt;
using System.Net.Sockets;
using System.Security.Claims;
using System.Security.Cryptography;
using System.Text;
using System.Threading.Tasks;
using TransforSerPu.Core.Dtos;
using TransforSerPu.Core.Interfaces;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{
    public class TokenService : ITokenService
    {
        
        private readonly ISecurityService _securityService;
        private readonly IUserService _userService;
        private readonly AuthenticationOptions _authenticationOptions;


        private string issuer;
        private string audience;
        private string secret;

        public TokenService(ISecurityService securityService,
            IOptions<AuthenticationOptions> authenticationOptions,
            IUserService userService)
        {
            _securityService = securityService;
            _authenticationOptions = authenticationOptions.Value;

            issuer = _authenticationOptions.Issuer;
            audience = _authenticationOptions.Audience;
            secret = _authenticationOptions.SecretKey;
            _userService = userService;
        }



        public async Task<AuthenticatedResponse> RenewToken(TokenDto tokenApiModel)
        {
            string accessToken = tokenApiModel.AccessToken;
            string refreshToken = tokenApiModel.RefreshToken;

            var principal = GetPrincipalFromExpiredToken(accessToken, secret);
            var username = principal.Identity.Name; //this is mapped to the Name claim by default

            var user = await _securityService.GetLoginByCredentials(new UserLoginDto() { User = username });

            var usuario = await _userService.GetUser(user.UserId);

            if (usuario == null || !usuario.IsActive )
                throw new BusinessException("Usuario inactivo.");

            if (user is null || user.RefreshToken != refreshToken || user.RefreshTokenExpiryTime <= DateTime.Now)
                throw new BusinessException("Credenciales equivocadas.");

            var newAccessToken = GenerateAccessToken(principal.Claims, issuer, audience, secret);
            var newRefreshToken = GenerateRefreshToken();

            user.RefreshToken = newRefreshToken;

            await _securityService.UpdateRefreshToken(username, newRefreshToken);

            return new AuthenticatedResponse()
            {
                AuthToken = newAccessToken,
                RefreshToken = newRefreshToken
            };
        }

        public string GenerateAccessToken(IEnumerable<Claim> claims, string issuer, string audience, string secret)
        {
            var secretKey = new SymmetricSecurityKey(Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(secret));
            var signinCredentials = new SigningCredentials(secretKey, SecurityAlgorithms.HmacSha256);

            var tokenOptions = new JwtSecurityToken(
                issuer: issuer,
                audience: audience,
                claims: claims,
                expires: DateTime.Now.AddHours(4),
                signingCredentials: signinCredentials
            );

            var tokenString = new JwtSecurityTokenHandler().WriteToken(tokenOptions);
            return tokenString;
        }

        public string GenerateRefreshToken()
        {
            var randomNumber = new byte[32];
            using (var rng = RandomNumberGenerator.Create())
            {
                rng.GetBytes(randomNumber);
                return Convert.ToBase64String(randomNumber);
            }
        }

        public ClaimsPrincipal GetPrincipalFromExpiredToken(string token, string secret)
        {
            var tokenValidationParameters = new TokenValidationParameters
            {
                ValidateAudience = false, //you might want to validate the audience and issuer depending on your use case
                ValidateIssuer = false,
                ValidateIssuerSigningKey = true,
                IssuerSigningKey = new SymmetricSecurityKey(Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(secret)),
                ValidateLifetime = false //here we are saying that we don't care about the token's expiration date
            };

            var tokenHandler = new JwtSecurityTokenHandler();
            SecurityToken securityToken;
            var principal = tokenHandler.ValidateToken(token, tokenValidationParameters, out securityToken);
            var jwtSecurityToken = securityToken as JwtSecurityToken;
            if (jwtSecurityToken == null || !jwtSecurityToken.Header.Alg.Equals(SecurityAlgorithms.HmacSha256, StringComparison.InvariantCultureIgnoreCase))
                throw new SecurityTokenException("Invalid token");

            return principal;
        }
    }
}

UserInRolesService.cs
************
﻿using Microsoft.Extensions.Options;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Linq;
using System.Text;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{
    public class UserInRolesService : IUserInRolesService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;

        public UserInRolesService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
        }

        public IEnumerable<UserInRoles> GetAll(Guid userId)
        {
            var barrios = _unitOfWork.UserInRolesRepository.Get(x => x.User, y => y.Rol)
                .Where(x => x.UserId == userId);
            return barrios;
        }

        public async Task InsertUserInRole(UserInRoles userInRole)
        {
            if (userInRole.UserId == Guid.Empty || userInRole.RolId == Guid.Empty)
                throw new BusinessException("UserId and RoleId are required");

            // Additional business validations if necessary

            await _unitOfWork.UserInRolesRepository.Insert(userInRole);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> UpdateUserInRole(UserInRoles userInRole)
        {
            var existingUserInRole = await _unitOfWork.UserInRolesRepository.GetById(userInRole.Id);
            if (existingUserInRole == null)
                throw new BusinessException("UserInRole doesn't exist");

            existingUserInRole.UserId = userInRole.UserId;
            existingUserInRole.RolId = userInRole.RolId;

            await _unitOfWork.UserInRolesRepository.Update(existingUserInRole);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<UserInRoles> GetUserInRole(Guid id)
        {
            return await _unitOfWork.UserInRolesRepository.GetById(id);
        }

        public PagedList<UserInRoles> GetUserInRoles(UserInRolesQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var userInRoles = _unitOfWork.UserInRolesRepository.Get(x => x.User, y => y.Rol);

            filters.PageNumber = filters.PageNumber;
            filters.PageSize = filters.PageSize;

            // Additional filtering logic if necessary

            var pagedUserInRoles = PagedList<UserInRoles>.Create(userInRoles, filters.PageNumber, filters.PageSize);

            return pagedUserInRoles;
        }

        public async Task DeleteUserInRole(Guid id)
        {
            await _unitOfWork.UserInRolesRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }
    }

}

---------------------------------------
UserService.cs
************
﻿using Microsoft.Extensions.Options;
using SocialMedia.Core.CustomEntities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;
using SocialMedia.Core.Exceptions;
using SocialMedia.Core.Interfaces;
using SocialMedia.Core.QueryFilters;
using System;
using System.Linq;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Services
{
    public class UserService : IUserService
    {
        private readonly IUnitOfWork _unitOfWork;
        private readonly PaginationOptions _paginationOptions;

        public UserService(IUnitOfWork unitOfWork, IOptions<PaginationOptions> paginationOptions)
        {
            _unitOfWork = unitOfWork;
            _paginationOptions = paginationOptions.Value;
        }

        public async Task InsertUser(User user)
        {
            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(user.Email))
                throw new BusinessException("Email is required");
            
            user.Id = Guid.NewGuid();
            // Additional business validations if necessary
            await _unitOfWork.UserRepository.Insert(user);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }

        public async Task<bool> UpdateUser(User user)
        {
            var existingUser = await _unitOfWork.UserRepository.GetById(user.Id);
            if (existingUser == null)
                throw new BusinessException("User doesn't exist");

            existingUser.FullName = user.FullName;
            existingUser.Email = user.Email;
            existingUser.Dni = user.Dni;
            existingUser.BornDate = user.BornDate;
            existingUser.Phone = user.Phone;
            existingUser.IsActive = user.IsActive;
            existingUser.Subscription = user.Subscription;

            await _unitOfWork.UserRepository.Update(existingUser);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
            return true;
        }

        public async Task<User> GetUser(Guid id)
        {
            return await _unitOfWork.UserRepository.GetById(id);
        }

        public PagedList<User> GetUsers(UserQueryFilter filters)
        {
            var users = _unitOfWork.UserRepository.Get();

            filters.PageNumber = filters.PageNumber;
            filters.PageSize = filters.PageSize;

            // Additional filtering logic if necessary
            if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(filters.Filter))
            {
                users = users.Where(x =>
                    x.Email.Contains(filters.Filter) ||
                    x.FullName.Contains(filters.Filter) ||
                    x.Phone.Contains(filters.Filter));
            }

            var pagedUsers = PagedList<User>.Create(users, filters.PageNumber, filters.PageSize);

            return pagedUsers;
        }

        public async Task DeleteUser(Guid id)
        {
            await _unitOfWork.UserRepository.Delete(id);
            await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        }
    }

}

---------------------------------------
Helper.cs
************
﻿using System;
using System.Collections;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Linq;
using System.Text;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace SocialMedia.Core.Utils
{
    public class Helper
    {
        public static void CopyProperties<TSource, TDestination>(TSource source, TDestination destination, List<string> excludedProperties = null)
        {
            var sourceProperties = typeof(TSource).GetProperties();
            var destinationProperties = typeof(TDestination).GetProperties();

            foreach (var sourceProperty in sourceProperties)
            {
                if (excludedProperties != null && excludedProperties.Contains(sourceProperty.Name))
                {
                    continue; // Saltar las propiedades excluidas
                }

                var destinationProperty = destinationProperties.FirstOrDefault(p => p.Name == sourceProperty.Name);

                if (destinationProperty != null && destinationProperty.PropertyType == sourceProperty.PropertyType)
                {
                    var sourceValue = sourceProperty.GetValue(source);
                    if (sourceValue != null && sourceValue.GetType().IsClass && sourceValue.GetType() != typeof(string))
                    {
                        // Propiedad es un objeto, aplicar copia recursiva
                        var destinationValue = Activator.CreateInstance(destinationProperty.PropertyType);
                        CopyProperties(sourceValue, destinationValue, excludedProperties);
                        destinationProperty.SetValue(destination, destinationValue);
                    }
                    else if (sourceValue is IList sourceList)
                    {
                        // Propiedad es una lista, aplicar copia recursiva a cada elemento
                        var destinationList = (IList)Activator.CreateInstance(destinationProperty.PropertyType);
                        foreach (var sourceItem in sourceList)
                        {
                            var destinationItem = Activator.CreateInstance(destinationList.GetType().GetGenericArguments()[0]);
                            CopyProperties(sourceItem, destinationItem, excludedProperties);
                            destinationList.Add(destinationItem);
                        }
                        destinationProperty.SetValue(destination, destinationList);
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        // Propiedad es un valor primitivo, copiar directamente
                        destinationProperty.SetValue(destination, sourceValue);
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        /*public static void CopyProperties<T>(T source, T destination, List<string> excludedProperties = null)
        {
            var sourceProperties = typeof(T).GetProperties();
            var destinationProperties = typeof(T).GetProperties();

            foreach (var sourceProperty in sourceProperties)
            {
                if (excludedProperties != null && excludedProperties.Contains(sourceProperty.Name))
                {
                    continue; // Saltar las propiedades excluidas
                }

                var destinationProperty = destinationProperties.FirstOrDefault(p => p.Name == sourceProperty.Name);

                if (destinationProperty != null && destinationProperty.PropertyType == sourceProperty.PropertyType)
                {
                    var sourceValue = sourceProperty.GetValue(source);
                    if (sourceValue != null && sourceValue.GetType().IsClass && sourceValue.GetType() != typeof(string))
                    {
                        // Propiedad es un objeto, aplicar copia recursiva
                        var destinationValue = Activator.CreateInstance(destinationProperty.PropertyType);
                        CopyProperties(sourceValue, destinationValue, excludedProperties);
                        destinationProperty.SetValue(destination, destinationValue);
                    }
                    else if (sourceValue is IList sourceList)
                    {
                        // Propiedad es una lista, aplicar copia recursiva a cada elemento
                        var destinationList = (IList)Activator.CreateInstance(destinationProperty.PropertyType);
                        foreach (var sourceItem in sourceList)
                        {
                            var destinationItem = Activator.CreateInstance(destinationList.GetType().GetGenericArguments()[0]);
                            CopyProperties(sourceItem, destinationItem, excludedProperties);
                            destinationList.Add(destinationItem);
                        }
                        destinationProperty.SetValue(destination, destinationList);
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        // Propiedad es un valor primitivo, copiar directamente
                        destinationProperty.SetValue(destination, sourceValue);
                    }
                }
            }
        }*/

    }
}

ActividadesSilviculturalesConfiguration.cs
************
﻿
using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;
using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Metadata.Builders;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;

namespace SocialMedia.Infrastructure.Data
{
    public class ActividadesSilviculturalesConfiguration : IEntityTypeConfiguration<ActividadesSilviculturales>
    {

        public void Configure(EntityTypeBuilder<ActividadesSilviculturales> builder)
        {
            builder.ToTable("ActividadesSilviculturales");

            builder.HasKey(e => e.Id);
            builder.Property(e => e.Id).HasColumnName("IdActividadesSilviculturales");

            builder.HasOne(a => a.CensoArboreo)
                .WithMany(c => c.ActividadesSilviculturales)
                .HasForeignKey(b => b.IdCensoArboreo)
                .HasConstraintName("FK_ACTIVIDADES_SILVICULTURALES_X_CENSO_ARBOREO");

        }
    }
}

---------------------------------------
CensoArboreoConfiguration.cs
************
﻿using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;
using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Metadata.Builders;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;

namespace SocialMedia.Infrastructure.Data
{
    public class CensoArboreoConfiguration : IEntityTypeConfiguration<CensoArboreo>
    {
        public void Configure(EntityTypeBuilder<CensoArboreo> builder)
        {
            builder.ToTable("CensoArboreo");

            builder.HasKey(e => e.Id);
            builder.Property(e => e.Id).HasColumnName("IdCensoArboreo");
           
        }
    }
}

---------------------------------------
CommentConfiguration.cs
************
﻿using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;
using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Metadata.Builders;
using SocialMedia.Core.Entities;

namespace SocialMedia.Infrastructure.Data
{
    public class CommentConfiguration : IEntityTypeConfiguration<Comment>
    {
        public void Configure(EntityTypeBuilder<Comment> builder)
        {
            builder.ToTable("Comentario");

            builder.HasKey(e => e.Id);

            builder.Property(e => e.Id)
                .HasColumnName("IdComentario").ValueGeneratedNever();

            builder.Property(e => e.PostId)
                .HasColumnName("IdPublicacion").ValueGeneratedNever();

            builder.Property(e => e.UserId)
                .HasColumnName("IdUsuario").ValueGeneratedNever();


            builder.HasOne(d => d.Post)
                .WithMany(p => p.Comments)
                .HasForeignKey(d => d.PostId)
                .OnDelete(DeleteBehavior.ClientSetNull)
                .HasConstraintName("FK_Comentario_Publicacion");

            builder.HasOne(d => d.User)
                .WithMany(p => p.Comments)
                .HasForeignKey(d => d.UserId)
                .OnDelete(DeleteBehavior.ClientSetNull)
                .HasConstraintName("FK_Comentario_Usuario");

         
        }
    }
}

﻿using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;
using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Metadata.Builders;

namespace SocialMedia.Infrastructure.Data
{
    public class DetalleConfiguration : IEntityTypeConfiguration<Detalle>
    {
        public void Configure(EntityTypeBuilder<Detalle> builder)
        {
            builder.ToTable("Detalle");

            builder.HasKey(e => e.Id);
            builder.Property(e => e.Id).HasColumnName("IdDetalle");

            builder
                .HasOne(a => a.Maestra)
                .WithMany(c => c.Detalles)
                .HasForeignKey(b => b.MaestraId)
                .HasConstraintName("FK_MAESTRA_X_DETALLE");
            ///ESPACIOS POTENCIALES
